Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请准备离船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,甲板上请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经抵达火烧岛松林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家来到火烧岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下船时请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,楼梯可能很滑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,另外请再次检查您的所有行李是否带齐...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,祝您一天愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 威克斯 - 嘿 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,露胸毛了哦 该到你了 泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我喜欢我的胸毛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,CK内裤不会赞同你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,棒球联赛已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的夏天正式到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是说到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 宝贝 - 你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冰啤? - 不了 我喝不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,条纹衫不赖啊 中尉 够性感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 叫人家队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,刚从纽联储回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,知道人们怎么说吗 我每个月都能当一次大款了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,最近没怎么在健身房看到你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到你了 布鲁斯 - 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁西 亲爱的 别让我们的海景别墅丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哦 不刮不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道人们怎么说吗 内德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不能打败他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就加入他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他没兴趣时 克雷格伤心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你看 他有了雷德福 (著名电影明星)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,说明上帝是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰还好吗? - 约翰?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰 - 噢 约翰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我现在和格里高利在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要庆祝我们的15月纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,15月? 对你来说很长了呀 米奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我们是情侣 住一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表我们需要对彼此忠贞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至不是犹太人 别跟我的犹太拉比说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 布鲁斯 你很烂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛还来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小说很破坏我们形象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看你周围 一片性解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说 太多的性爱会让寻找真爱变得不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别把你的情路失败找不到对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 发泄在我们身上 - 内迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢! - 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗? - 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我能站起来 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是有一点... 晕眩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,祝亲爱的克雷格生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吹!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他的强项哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈爱死这地方了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"You Make Me Feel" (Mighty Real)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,内德! 嘿 内德!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我卖过一只陶瓷猪给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴勒克大街的法国艺术馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫桑福德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个朋友在收集猪艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而你有除真猪外我所见过最大的猪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在越变越大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不肯消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她的第20个病人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有6个死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 内德 很快就到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,巴兹 我不知道你在这儿上班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,内德·威克斯 "时报"文章后我联络过你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来问一些问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是同志 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那就脱衣服 别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过的男体比你都多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说 关于你那些问题 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没听过或见过这样的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你有任何症状吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"时报"上写的大多数东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,阿米巴虫 淋病 肝炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂性革命后我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么让你觉得我不懂的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有发烧 盗汗 体重减轻吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,做梦都想呢 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,紫斑呢? 张开嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是种癌症
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让免疫系统产生奇怪反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它崩溃了 不肯免疫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我的很多病人都被普通疾病击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而那些细菌原本是连婴儿都伤害不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总之纽约市的婴儿不会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,免疫系统是我们了解得最少的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你有大嘴巴 它在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大嘴巴是症状? - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这种病似乎只发生在男同身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,巴兹说你在同志群体中很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想到什么就说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到任何同志领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我联系了同志组织 可没人回我电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁克娜医生 只要有一半脑子的人都不会想牵扯进同志政治
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有指责的余地 - 你想指责什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦了我们扮受害人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中的绝大多数人都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在正用得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们在等一个人来领导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想领导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想要试着说服我做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟男同志说停止做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这个癌症是通过性来传播?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能证明吗 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你能意识到你在说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是上百万的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看重滥交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并且把它作为一个基本政治纲领吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要怎么应对? - 跟他们说可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪儿? - 大厅尽头 大厅尽头!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这么简单 比这个要复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为性就是他们的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,威克斯先生 如果做爱会杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,任何只要有一半脑子的人会不停止做爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了 我没在你身上看到我想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪儿? - 开门!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪儿? 哪儿? - 那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把他放在桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿 我来查脉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别动 - 能告诉我发生了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在外面跟他会合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚转过街角 他就发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老天!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚到路边去!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的天! - 救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁是他的爱人? - 是我 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么? - 布鲁斯·奈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是布鲁克娜 我现在就需要一间病房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奈尔斯 你曾是莱因哈特的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 女士 你怎么知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他三周前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至不让我跟他道别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不让我跟他吻别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它有这么快吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的假设只是建立在46个病例上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道我怎么想 这就是我怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全部会交叉传染
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有一部分人这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾的是 我们无法辨别哪些感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早在我们隔离出肝炎病毒前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也知道它们会带来什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么传播的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,医学期刊怎么说? "时报"呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一年前就把第一份报告寄给医学期刊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你怎么知道你要找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你不知道你要找什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 可能我的这个问题很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不蠢 这是最聪明的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是回答它最难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,常识没有告诉你们 可以停止做爱一阵子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这就没给我们多少盼头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,万一事实证明你错了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让她说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟的情形就是你们停止做爱一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这不是可能最糟的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人们会害怕做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会失去长久以来通过斗争换得的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会成为最糟糕的替罪羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界会认为我们是携带者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,道德多数派绝对会开心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个轮椅贱人不走我就不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我看过的病人一周比一周多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有一半病人已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她是说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道新罗谢尔市正有个群交派对在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,卫生部在哪儿? 市长在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭上他妈的嘴 约翰 - 闭上你他妈的嘴 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,数据是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,每个同志会议都是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一半人到场是为了约炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,安静! 安静!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要成立一个组织 我们要成立一个健康危机组织
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会再在这儿聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下次准备些该死的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿 这可不礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎参与同志政治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我和克雷格·克莱波恩有个重要会面 我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 菲尼克斯·特勒 - 你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫内德·威克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你非常帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你找上我的时间不合适 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我有交稿截止日期 第一夫人来纽约了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你是同志 而且你可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会帮我在"时报"登出一些重要信息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你"听说"? 听谁说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 亲爱的 人人都在说好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么每个同志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都觉得是我在经营”纽约时报"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法帮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉听到 那你建议我怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自己选吧 我写过23个派对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,37家新餐厅 12家新迪斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我没法让这儿任何人再写一篇相关报道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟半打记者聊过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,包括那个写第一篇报道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"皮革先生"? 不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿没人会写这个 我也不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我们这里分工很细
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想科学专栏来写羊毛衫 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我感觉非常荒谬的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须求助于直人的世界来报道一点同志的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是碰巧写同志设计师 同志迪斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,同志大厨 同志模特 同志摇滚明星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有同志名人 同志一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不叫他们同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正好是时候开始啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个交稿日期在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不想我被炒鱿鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样的人最给我蛋疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你写书的? - 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 哥们 关注同志癌啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 关注同志癌? 不吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 关注同志癌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 关注同志癌吗? 在同志社群中有一种癌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能关注一下同志癌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一场…我们社群正在经历一场危机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的用得到...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用得到你们的帮助 好吗? 不?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以少一点点进攻性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,少一点进攻性? 我们试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,能关注一下我们社群发生的癌症吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 关注同志癌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 关注同志癌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很可笑 我妈妈送了花来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至没跟她说过我是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我只跟她说克雷格死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为妈妈们总是能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在一套房子上面花5百万你不感到害怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,光是让你来打理我的财务都让我心惊肉跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要买房的话随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这提醒了我 你的帐户需要更多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上你干得不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀念你投身电影业的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我喜欢电影 - 我嗅到被否定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大哥刚管我从事的是”柠檬”? (次品的意思)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想购房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那你干嘛一直在郊区晃荡?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个人住不好玩 - 这个布鲁斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在和他交往吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得到他 他看不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,本…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的律所能免费接下这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说 无偿代理?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成立了一个组织 我跟你说过有种新疾病…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这听上去像又一个让你停止写作的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么就不能直接说"好"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了 因为我们有内部委员会来决定这类事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可你是高级合伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 马里奥 霍默还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不肯帮忙 我只能找其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎你找其他人 - 我不想找其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我大哥的气派 有名 一流 大型的律所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,成为纽约市第一家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,无偿代理同志事业的直人律所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为它 为你感到无比的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,下一次会议我会让其他合伙人通过它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去游说 你听上去不像会投赞成票的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的反应有进步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我每周都在增加3到4个新病人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,7个进了重症监护室 整个医院只有30个床位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们当中有的人被检查出其他病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有20个人住了承担不起的私人病房
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那些没有医疗保险的人呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艺术家 演员? - 他们中有8个住在另一间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该安排他们住的病房
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不戴手套和面罩?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不戴 永远不打算戴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,结果我仍然在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么所有食物都这样摆在病房外?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它们会变冷 - 它们总是冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当值的工作人员不肯送进房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以食物就在外面发霉 直到我的人员经手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿 嗯 就在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 通过隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.63,0:22:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,通过隧道 把书放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识他 我可以和你一起进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你穿上那些保护件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不穿 我也不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿 换一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 听到我说的了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听到我说的了吗 往回走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 桑福德 - 看到了吗 走隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,往前开 穿过它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样 士兵?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见我的狗 能带我的狗来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我它没法生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见我的狗 我想见我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直走 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 不 把书放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿 用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能把我的狗带来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我它没法生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会带我的狗来?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它叫跳跳 你叫它它就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想它了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你19岁时能想象这些吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的第一个男友 你打算和他厮守终生的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是修电视的?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请去407室修一下电视
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我拒绝进去 - 修电视 这是你他妈的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工会说 我不需要冒生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,去服务一些会传染的娘泡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果非要我进去 我就他妈的不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.31,0:24:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的工会到底又在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来点这个吗? 还是啤酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 啤酒就可以 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.39,0:25:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她叫珊姆 - 嗨 珊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 我以前真的喜欢高科技装潢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.63,0:25:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望印花布能回归
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.26,0:25:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别觉得我说话冲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.90,0:25:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望印花布能回归
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,两个希望印花布回归的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.44,0:25:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这真的是一个约会
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你高兴我来吗? - 噢...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.49,0:25:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来我高兴得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.12,0:25:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你很帅气 你在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己丑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.89,0:25:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪儿的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.19,0:25:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,俄克拉荷马州
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.83,0:26:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我18岁时离开家 自己供自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你要跳舞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,自己供自己念了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.30,0:26:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸在西塔尔萨市的炼油厂上班
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈是女招待
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在沃尔格林药店有一个快餐摊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.98,0:26:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很了不起 不是吗? 一个小鬼从这一切冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.75,0:26:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最后走进"时报"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥整个世界的品位与时尚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.95,0:26:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终于开始好好说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.79,0:26:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说不是我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴才是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.26,0:26:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛写那些花哨舞裙玩意儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说你每天都会盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.83,0:26:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的人已经有10个死了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.60,0:26:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在我去找你的时候 还只有1个
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.27,0:26:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才同意这个约会的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.95,0:26:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,叉在左边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.85,0:27:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,刀在右边
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.42,0:27:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,知道希特勒灭绝犹太人的"最后解决方案"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.96,0:27:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次被"时报"提及是在哪儿吗? 第28版
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.30,0:27:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"华盛顿邮报" 第6版
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.30,0:27:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,两家都是犹太人的报纸 自己人的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.03,0:27:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,学者们终于开始如实记叙了 每个人都被拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,基督教会在哪儿? 教皇? 丘吉尔? 罗斯福?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.81,0:27:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们当中任何人说些什么都会警告希特勒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.81,0:27:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,达豪集中营1933年开张的 所有人都他妈的在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.95,0:27:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这一晚看来会变得非常浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没有过爱人 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你有过不少
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我有过一个很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.26,0:27:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在一起很多年 所以谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.89,0:27:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他比我大 找到了个更年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是恋父吗? - 不 我没有恋父情结 上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.54,0:28:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有无数理由不牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.52,0:28:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,美国犹太人完全知道在发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象如果每个犹太人都骄傲的去华盛顿游行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.92,0:28:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,内德
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得我了 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.26,0:28:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是几年前 在浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.93,0:28:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来男国 看看我们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.64,0:28:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能提供什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.67,0:28:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,男国是一家设施齐全 多层套式的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.71,0:28:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为每个人个性化服务而设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.94,0:28:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以来男国强健身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.48,0:28:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或是与其他人发展友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来过一次你就会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.77,0:29:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我的样子 就像我是在申请加入中情局
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟着你走进你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.16,0:29:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至没睁开你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说你的真名叫亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.44,0:29:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你是做什么的 结果你说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.21,0:29:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你"做过各种事情" 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.58,0:29:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我问有没有包括爱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时你说 "我早上还要早起呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,男人不是天生不去爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.83,0:30:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是学会了不去爱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.80,0:30:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你在伪装自己
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会不记得你?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.00,0:30:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当时很黑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们可以重新开始吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.22,0:30:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.07,0:31:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我上耶鲁的时候 我以为我是那儿唯一的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.84,0:31:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看想改造我的心理医生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.41,0:31:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结果有了"同志威克斯"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.45,0:31:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他比那儿的任何人都会跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.22,0:31:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下如果能在最美好的大学时光
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.92,0:31:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和你的男友脸贴脸跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.33,0:31:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你有跟女人睡过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.60,0:31:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫...黛利拉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.34,0:31:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,黛利拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.71,0:31:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.34,0:32:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我写的一部电影的替身演员
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她人很好 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,经常对我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.02,0:32:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以… 我让一个直人朋友教了我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.79,0:32:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我知道 但我只想确认
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.73,0:32:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我请她共用晚餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我觉得到合适时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.70,0:32:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我一直在给下面做工作...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.00,0:32:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"你准备好了吗? 你确定准备好了吗?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.04,0:32:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当我的"独角兽"像是准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我把她抱起来 非常白瑞德 ("乱世佳人"男主角)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.18,0:32:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把她放在我的床上
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.01,0:32:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后就软了 - 噢!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可是... - 我能体会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.95,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在半夜的时候 我醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,胯下肿涨得惊人 天知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.82,0:32:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我推醒她 大叫 "求你了 帮我把它塞进去 黛利拉"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.79,0:32:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕它会在我找到...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.03,0:32:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能够放进去的合适地方前软了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.47,0:33:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她做了 我做了 我的独角兽做了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.01,0:33:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早上我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.11,0:33:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一直生活在那个下决心要改造我的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.61,0:33:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,心理医生的魔咒里的我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,冲进他的办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个从7年级起一直干男人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.82,0:33:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在32岁时歇斯底里的宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.13,0:33:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"吉里斯皮医生 我不再是处男了!”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.04,0:33:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这儿 我们应该能碰到他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.31,0:33:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.48,0:33:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就走过去打招呼?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.42,0:33:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他说我邀请了你 我们一起念的耶鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.28,0:33:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是我的送行派对 他能把我怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.62,0:33:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.69,0:33:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,市长希望您消失
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.99,0:34:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我的朋友 内德·威克斯 - 我们知道他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.13,0:34:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,市长先生! 我们需要你的帮助!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,新的疾病正在流行 你一定听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.57,0:34:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们亟需你的帮助! 放开我 混球些!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.37,0:34:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是美国!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.87,0:34:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,市长先生! 我们正在死去!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.91,0:34:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 这是内德写给我们准备投递的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.45,0:34:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"我受够了人们哀号要放弃滥交…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这让他们比死还难受
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.42,0:34:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了人们只用阴茎来思考
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.22,0:34:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了深柜的同志 1982年了 伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.93,0:34:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候出柜? 到1983年你们可能已经死了"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.83,0:34:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.03,0:34:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 布鲁斯? 你真这么觉得?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.77,0:34:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚不是该选出一个主席吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能教人们怎么过他们的生活 内德
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.77,0:34:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,整个同志政治运动都是关于做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.51,0:34:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.68,0:34:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我对为病人提供一些服务项目更感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.91,0:34:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该开始谈谈他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.71,0:34:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,另外还有很多担惊受怕的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.42,0:35:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们格外需要信息
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.85,0:35:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想开办一条热线
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.09,0:35:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 他还不知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.22,0:35:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫汤米·鲍特莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.69,0:35:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现实中他是一位医院主任
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.43,0:35:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来帮忙的 而且是个南方骚婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.10,0:35:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍特莱特先生 我是布鲁斯·奈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.23,0:35:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴认识你 - 我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.77,0:35:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.94,0:35:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.74,0:35:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.64,0:35:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的主意吗 内德?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.84,0:35:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在看 但我看不到问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.48,0:35:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续看 - 我们附的回邮地址
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说就因为信封上有"同志"这个词吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.72,0:35:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,正他妈是 为什么不只是我们的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.65,0:35:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们不能投递这些 - 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们希望有人来参加这个舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.56,0:35:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须在今晚投递它们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.19,0:35:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要用荧光笔涂掉"同志"这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.26,0:35:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 涂一万次?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯 我同情那些仍然和父母
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,居住在长岛的孩子 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.67,0:35:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那些会收到这些信的人... 看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你有家... 你一个人住 拥有自己的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.14,0:35:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈住在另一个州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.74,0:35:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的邮差知道了怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.04,0:36:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是要我觉得你是认真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.81,0:36:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是认真的 内德 - 好了 女士们 乖乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.25,0:36:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 已经很晚了 我们仍然没有一个主席
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.82,0:36:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,内迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.98,0:36:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该是布鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.72,0:36:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都认识他 每个人都喜欢他 每个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.96,0:36:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他人缘好 而每个人都怕我?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.85,0:36:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.89,0:36:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看他嘛 他…帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.99,0:36:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所有克里斯朵夫街和火烧岛的小鬼 (均为同性恋聚集地)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.93,0:36:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们感觉会更舒服 假如跟随他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.57,0:36:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就跟高中一样 - 是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.73,0:36:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 所有支持布鲁斯·奈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.67,0:36:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我们主席的人 请举手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.11,0:36:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.74,0:36:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你帅呆了 我们都会跟随你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干你 我接受了 - 干你 恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.21,0:37:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 让我们搬到很远
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.81,0:37:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们俩 一起去一个无人的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.91,0:37:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能停下一秒钟不去想事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.99,0:37:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激你没有吼我 关于"时报"的不作为
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.22,0:37:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的不够政治性 你为什么没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.91,0:37:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不用和某个人谈政治其实是一种解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.40,0:37:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.43,0:37:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你就像一个不真实的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.20,0:37:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我这辈子都在等一个像你这样的爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.67,0:37:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你终于出现
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.31,0:37:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕自己做出什么蠢事把它搞砸害怕到死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.51,0:37:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是不是疯子? - 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.35,0:37:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.19,0:37:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.35,0:38:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.41,0:39:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能看出我化了很厚的妆吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看着好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.56,0:39:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须去艾玛那儿看看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.46,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能忘了这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.09,0:39:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.03,0:39:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不好我也不想知道 因为没人会用我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.53,0:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而如果我不能工作 我还不如死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.04,0:39:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我体重有下降吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.51,0:39:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我跟你说过别告诉他的 - 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已经害怕和我接吻了?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.99,0:39:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.83,0:39:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我还害怕过给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.91,0:40:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.85,0:40:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我送他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.09,0:40:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 他是我交往的第三个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.46,0:40:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,莱因哈特 克雷格 现在我不知道自己能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.93,0:40:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,假如埃尔伯特也得了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.43,0:40:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你得战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.94,0:40:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.41,0:40:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友 内德·威克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.94,0:40:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友 我没见过其他像你这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.95,0:40:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 像我这样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.25,0:40:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,像你 就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.42,0:40:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的老家 我是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.05,0:40:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我参军我才见到活的犹太人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.99,0:40:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说一个...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.49,0:40:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.49,0:40:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,风趣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.27,0:41:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好看的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.57,0:41:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友不再跟我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.01,0:41:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们说我让他们扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.14,0:41:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.72,0:41:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不怎么像犹太人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不怎么像同志
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.59,0:41:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们都可以作为白人蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.77,0:41:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱埃尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.77,0:41:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯 看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.44,0:41:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.51,0:41:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔伯特会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.11,0:41:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,万一有事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.95,0:41:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.03,0:42:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我真是一团糟 - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.85,0:42:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 经典一刻啊 - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.97,0:42:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没事 - 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当我和你终于变得我想要这样的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.05,0:43:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不想要和你这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.53,0:43:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯 我也恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.07,0:43:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.74,0:43:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,见他的鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,变装皇后坐镇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.41,0:43:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它想要的时候还真管用
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.16,0:43:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 菲尼克斯 这是迪克·伦巴多
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.43,0:43:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 我们的董事会终于有了个
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.93,0:43:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不迷恋迪斯科的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.56,0:43:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许今晚除外
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.56,0:43:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 稍后见 - 很高兴认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.53,0:43:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.61,0:44:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"I will survive" (Gloria Gaynor)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.48,0:44:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我们非常开心有你们加入!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.21,0:44:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们证明我们不只是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,外貌 头脑 才华 和心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.49,0:44:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们募集到了本市任何一个同志组织都没有募集过的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.93,0:44:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请他上来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.13,0:44:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,内德·威克斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.26,0:45:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.11,0:45:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.54,0:45:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们要宣布募集到多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.74,0:45:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.95,0:45:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,五万三千块!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.57,0:45:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,男同志健康危机组织 都上来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.44,0:45:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 亲爱的 上来 请上来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.54,0:45:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.78,0:45:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让咱们跳吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.30,0:46:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪有一天他会来♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.04,0:46:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我爱的男人♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.51,0:46:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪他会高大又强壮♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.41,0:46:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我爱的男人♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.12,0:46:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♪当他朝我走来♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.89,0:46:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我会尽我的所能♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.22,0:46:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪只为让他留下来♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.40,0:46:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪他会看着我微笑♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.07,0:46:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我能理解♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.61,0:46:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪就在一小会儿后♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.11,0:46:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♪他会牵我的手♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.68,0:47:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪尽管看上去可笑♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.32,0:47:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我知道我们都不会有片言♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.06,0:47:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♪也许我该见他 在星期天♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.07,0:47:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪也许在星期一♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.94,0:47:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪也许不会♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.71,0:47:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我仍然确信要见他...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.85,0:47:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想象如果我们年轻时就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.45,0:47:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有恐惧 没有羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.95,0:47:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想象那些年都是和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.99,0:47:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪他会建造一个小小的家♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.96,0:47:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪就住两个人♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.70,0:47:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我永远也不再流浪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.27,0:48:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪是你 你会?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.81,0:48:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪所以重要过一切♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.15,0:48:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我在等那个男人...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.75,0:48:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯·特勒 你愿意搬来和我同住吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.05,0:48:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.65,0:48:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的? - 真的 就今天
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.09,0:48:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,耶! 耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.09,0:48:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,♪所以重要过一切…♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.40,0:48:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我在等那个男人♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.00,0:48:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我爱的男人♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.62,0:48:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是活动的定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.99,0:48:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等待着不管什么将我们引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.20,0:48:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:49:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这篇文章还没把你吓得半死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.47,0:49:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,男同志在地球上就没有明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.13,0:49:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的存在取决于你们能有多么愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拒绝给我们提供外籍急症室
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.16,0:49:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快进来!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.03,0:49:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他好像失去神智了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.81,0:49:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 我要把他放哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.71,0:49:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放在沙发上 我打给艾玛
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.24,0:49:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈的! - 我去倒水
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.78,0:49:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他这样多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.39,0:49:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.66,0:49:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你问了我这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.93,0:49:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么想? 我觉得政府
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.63,0:49:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在故意忽视这个流行病
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.23,0:49:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在指控美利坚合众国政府
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.34,0:49:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,密谋杀害所有同性恋?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.98,0:49:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的 你可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.35,0:49:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 萨拉伯丝 我就是这意思 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.38,0:49:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个很严重的指控啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.08,0:49:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有一场流行病
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.19,0:50:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而它被美利坚合众国政府所忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.29,0:50:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 故意的? - 故意的忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是国家紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.29,0:50:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是场大流行病 是一场瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.13,0:50:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能在国家电视台指控政府谋杀 内德
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.16,0:50:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么不? - 因为有天我们会需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.97,0:50:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,研究 拨款
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.39,0:50:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,国会仍然没有批准一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.30,0:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,市长仍然置若罔闻
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 你在公开场合没有任何权利代言这家机构
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.21,0:50:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们事先批准你要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.38,0:50:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 你甚至不是这个机构的管理层
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.98,0:50:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全不应该代言我们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.18,0:50:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢跟我分享这个 迪克 (有混球意思)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.83,0:50:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得为什么这个城市这么迟缓
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.57,0:50:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,承认和应对这个紧急状况?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.50,0:50:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在暗示这个城市已经承认
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:50:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个紧急状况了 马尔科姆 它没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.14,0:50:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得为什么没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.04,0:50:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为市长是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.58,0:51:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他对自己的遮羞布被扯掉怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.98,0:51:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.55,0:51:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关掉 关掉镜头 - 还在直播吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.88,0:51:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只代言自己的时候 你不能决定我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.52,0:51:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,扯淡 大家都知道你是我们的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是完全的政治错误
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能称呼某个没有宣布自己性向的人是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.43,0:51:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道应该是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.06,0:51:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在是特殊情况 我们正在死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.43,0:51:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,市长 他是你的私人朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.23,0:51:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望他任命你当法官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.07,0:51:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这里存在一点利益冲突吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.27,0:51:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我跟你说过我把备忘录发他了 - 什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.90,0:51:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 透过我的关系 - 什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会回答我 - 什么时候?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.27,0:51:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这个月新增了110个病例!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.61,0:51:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们仍然不能和我们的同志市长会面
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.18,0:51:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不能和他的同志助理会面
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.85,0:51:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 我给你难堪了吗 布鲁斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.12,0:51:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你给了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.45,0:51:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,胡萝卜比大棒有更好效果 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.72,0:51:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝 没人这么教过我 汤米
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.12,0:51:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,显然他们没有
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.23,0:51:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我也不怎么信这套鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.96,0:51:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在全部在做的是试着帮我们的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.96,0:51:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 请你大声跟内德念一下这份报告好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.10,0:51:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们训练了25位危机辅导员
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.07,0:52:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助新确诊的病人获得任何可能需要的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.91,0:52:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有12位团队领袖 和这些辅导员
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.54,0:52:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每周至少见一次面 查看他们的病人情况
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.64,0:52:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有17位志愿社工
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.45,0:52:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,心理学家和(或)心理医生
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.02,0:52:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经帮助起草了75份遗嘱...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.65,0:52:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,75 布鲁斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.42,0:52:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前曾经是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.12,0:52:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢在特种部队的日子吗? - 是的 我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.06,0:52:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经完全忘记怎么去战斗了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.09,0:52:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我说怎么去战斗 我只是和你的战斗方式不同
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.70,0:52:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没有看到你的方式 - 没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.66,0:52:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯...埃尔伯特就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.40,0:52:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混球! 你敢再说他一个字!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.30,0:52:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.04,0:52:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.94,0:52:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全没有资格进这个董事会
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.51,0:52:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你给你的市长朋友施加压力
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我最开始邀你加入的原因 你自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.59,0:52:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我不做 - 为什么不?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.70,0:53:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经从我的律所得到免费法律服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.43,0:53:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要进你的董事会
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.20,0:53:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是象征意义的 你不需要做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.57,0:53:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在逃避 如果它是个直人病...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.64,0:53:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这和你是同志没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.92,0:53:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那它还和什么有关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.01,0:53:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,迟早有一天 我会让你认同
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.38,0:53:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个国家超过两千万的男女同性恋
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.58,0:53:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要去接受心理医生辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.38,0:53:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,试着理解我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.68,0:53:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我有看报 看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.88,0:53:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那些男的穿皮革 链子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.89,0:53:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,裙子 高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.65,0:53:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟自己说 "内德不是这样的”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.49,0:53:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道媒体总是极端戏剧化一切
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.29,0:53:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有非常糟糕的形象问题
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.49,0:53:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你这样的人支持我们才这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.43,0:53:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经有你的威望了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.13,0:53:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好现在就吃午饭 我有个重要会议
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.73,0:53:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有吗? 多重要?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.94,0:53:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我在请求你的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.57,0:53:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有我觉得重要的事上 你都得到我的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.67,0:53:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而在我唯一觉得重要的事上
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.14,0:53:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全没有你的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.08,0:53:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在你内心深处某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.15,0:53:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是觉得我有病 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.42,0:53:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你很好适应了生活
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.18,0:54:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难怪了 - 我看过你有多么不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.59,0:54:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.19,0:54:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不得不看心理医生 我们并肩成长起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.93,0:54:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对爸爸和妈妈都有同样体会
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.70,0:54:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认我有一大堆可怕的性格缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.07,0:54:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不承认是他们对我们做过的可怕事情
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.90,0:54:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我生病和变同性恋 而你依然健康和异性恋的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.74,0:54:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对一些事情的反应不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.84,0:54:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你成了律师 我成了作家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.21,0:54:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有不同的理论分歧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.41,0:54:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你的理论把我看成一个火星来客
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.12,0:54:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的理论不这么看你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.58,0:54:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在暗示我做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.92,0:54:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不该在你那么小就送你去看医生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.22,0:54:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你会永远留在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.76,0:54:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没觉得自己做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.46,0:54:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你送我去那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.43,0:54:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,本 你对我来说比世界上任何人都重要
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.27,0:54:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一直如此 本 你得说出来 - 说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.77,0:54:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一样 说出来 说啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.08,0:55:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.61,0:55:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.75,0:55:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.86,0:55:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,每次输掉这场争论 都让我更受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.89,0:55:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我回家了 - 别这样 柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.29,0:55:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我依然爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.93,0:55:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉依然爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.43,0:55:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们的猫依然爱你 - 这不是一个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.60,0:55:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你有我的爱 我的法律服务 我的财务监督
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.84,0:55:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法给你站在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.07,0:55:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说你根本他妈不在乎我是怎么想的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.91,0:55:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都会在别人那儿受挫
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.68,0:55:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是哪种形式的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.38,0:55:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中大多数人学会怎么克服它 不管别人怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.58,0:55:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有没有别人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.55,0:55:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,停止再从我这儿撩起什么负罪感
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.32,0:55:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要我认同你生下来就和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救不了你快死的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.69,0:55:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这恰恰是能救我快死的朋友的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.33,0:55:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的口气就像我是你的敌人 - 我开始觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.27,0:55:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你的直人世界才是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.67,0:55:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你出离愤怒!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.94,0:56:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还有所有让我觉得爱上男人是病的该死的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.27,0:56:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我在试着理解
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.38,0:56:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没人他妈的在乎我们正在死去!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.51,0:56:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一个五百万的房子? 我们甚至从市政府领不到27分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.85,0:56:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的人有43个死了 你说这是我的事业不是你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.39,0:56:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然觉得我有病
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.13,0:56:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也没办法忍受一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.30,0:56:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再和你讲话 直到你接受我作为和你一样的对等!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.57,0:56:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一样健康的对等!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.37,0:56:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的弟弟!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.98,0:56:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 男孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是珍贵古董 - 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.35,0:56:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想我们是不是该把它放进沙龙间
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.35,0:56:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有地下室吗? 我觉得它该去那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.19,0:56:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,贝拉 我觉得是时候让你的臭嘴见天日了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.82,0:56:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天再来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.92,0:56:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们先尽可能把它摁进去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.69,0:57:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.40,0:57:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 别闹了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.10,0:57:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.17,0:57:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 嗨 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.50,0:57:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫埃斯特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.74,0:57:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友哈维昨晚死了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.01,0:57:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪儿都在一起 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.71,0:57:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,比如去百老汇 看火箭女郎歌舞
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.58,0:57:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,溜冰
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.12,0:57:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他溜得好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.12,0:57:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.96,0:57:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可他不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.63,0:57:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经那么的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.70,0:57:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 我想做点什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.37,0:57:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕我所有拉拉朋友都说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.97,0:57:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“你们又为我们做过什么?”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.77,0:57:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.44,0:57:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就当这是为了哈维
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.58,0:57:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 告诉我可以用到我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.76,0:58:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个热线主管 你觉得可以做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.06,0:58:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道怎么做 - 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.03,0:58:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.23,0:58:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让我给你买杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.44,0:58:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后我们再想办法 好吗? - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.28,0:58:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以你想架在这儿? - 是的 这儿很好 我们拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.35,0:58:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们在干嘛? - 我们是NBC下属台的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.26,0:58:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以? - 这里是新的男同健康危机办公室吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.92,0:58:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是谁? - 我是布鲁斯·奈尔斯 我是主席
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.66,0:58:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有签署任何允许拍我或这家机构的同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.43,0:58:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请立刻关掉镜头 - 别碰我的摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.53,0:58:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁派你来的? - 一个叫内德的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.84,0:58:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 威克斯 - 噢 太好了 你们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.91,0:58:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有基佬吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.41,0:58:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,混球
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.71,0:58:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,镜头在拍吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.38,0:59:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快看 同一周的两本杂志都有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.55,0:59:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每家主流电视网络
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.41,0:59:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在终于有第一间我们的办公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.02,0:59:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们介绍我们还在柜子里的同志主席
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.19,0:59:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他是那么帅气 你们不觉得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.52,0:59:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这么帅气的封面男孩浪费了多可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.43,0:59:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 现在你要战斗了 战斗啊 布鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.28,0:59:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我说得像个懦夫 我不是懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.47,0:59:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗? 你没有什么可失去的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.13,0:59:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥替你投资 所以你有收入
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.24,0:59:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以一天24小时当同志 内德 可是我不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.11,0:59:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行! 所以去你妈的!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.77,0:59:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 去你妈的 布鲁斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.94,0:59:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.91,0:59:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看着你 我充满了失望
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.58,0:59:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看着你 我担心我们不可能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.09,0:59:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这个国家是建立在什么上?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.09,0:59:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为它是从保罗·列维尔开始的 (警告美国人民反抗英军的报信人)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.26,0:59:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.96,0:59:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 看着我 看着我!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.43,0:59:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.23,0:59:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果照你的方式 我们就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.37,1:00:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 完了! - 怎么要人们帮我们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.97,1:00:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,假如他们不知道我们是谁?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.24,1:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了我们是谁 他们就不会帮我们 内德
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.71,1:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.62,1:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见鬼 - 见鬼!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.97,1:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我来接好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.24,1:00:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂? 你是我们接的第一个热线电话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.61,1:00:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能为你做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.74,1:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你打错了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.22,1:00:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现在就需要好好拾掇一下 知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.45,1:00:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你需要停止做个抓马女王 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.59,1:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是埃斯特拉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.57,1:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.95,1:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“More than this” (Roxy Music)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我们有四只手 两份收入
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.75,1:02:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会再变年轻
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.19,1:02:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别扯上我的年纪
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.97,1:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 郊区很美 - 郊区很安静
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.37,1:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 你敢接
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.61,1:02:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须接
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.94,1:02:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别说你在答录机上留了这里的号码
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.48,1:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你保证过 - 喂?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.35,1:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实觉得我们该针对市长
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.38,1:02:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我说的 而且我坚持原话 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.45,1:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你保证过
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.92,1:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 等着
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.70,1:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,任何男同志如果不站出来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.83,1:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和为挽救自己的生命而战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.30,1:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上都在帮助杀害剩下的我们
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.77,1:02:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要死多少人才能让你吓到半死
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.37,1:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做点什么? 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.95,1:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听说它们叫”承受内德愤怒的学校”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.39,1:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我们一个科学报道的记者谈过了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.69,1:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.06,1:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他是同志 他不肯...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.26,1:03:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别吼我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.63,1:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那些心理医生 他们也不是一无是处
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.93,1:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞特沃医生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.54,1:03:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马勒夫医生 - 马勒夫啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.71,1:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吉勒斯皮医生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.34,1:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帕蒂医生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.88,1:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克辛医生 拉弗恩医生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.31,1:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要我说这么久?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.05,1:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你只知道吃甜品
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.35,1:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,糖是生活中最重要的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.92,1:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其他一切只是存活
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.73,1:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.27,1:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 该死的董事会
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.03,1:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我在制造恐慌 自己想出风头
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.10,1:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没人愿意接受采访或上电视
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.31,1:04:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才自动接手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.74,1:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你成为了领袖
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.08,1:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而你是好斗的 - 我好斗? 我吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.48,1:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你? 正是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.65,1:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.82,1:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.35,1:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很讽刺 我从没想过当一个领袖
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.82,1:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我做得不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.79,1:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜我们失去了那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.13,1:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那时还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.57,1:04:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,假如我染上了...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.24,1:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你会离开我吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.72,1:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.96,1:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,换作是我 你会吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.29,1:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.73,1:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.33,1:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我母亲是地方红十字会的会长
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.17,1:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从我8岁起她就让我在采血车上工作
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.44,1:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我天生适合做这个
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.24,1:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 有件事我得告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.78,1:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于怀上了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.55,1:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我结过一次婚
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.72,1:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你没跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.79,1:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.09,1:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我对她不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.89,1:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那时确实是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.00,1:05:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有一个儿子 - 你有一个儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.97,1:05:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她不让我见他 - 你不能见自己的儿子?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.64,1:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你有反抗吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.24,1:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那说明你感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.91,1:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他迟早也会
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.18,1:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我不告诉你的原因 谁说我没反抗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.48,1:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,内德?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.38,1:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果别人没有你希望的那么坚强怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.35,1:05:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,软弱能吓得我屁滚尿流!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.69,1:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲就软弱 我害怕自己变成他
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.86,1:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他这辈子什么也不是 然后就结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.83,1:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不停战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.86,1:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白如果我做得到
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.56,1:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么别人就做不到 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.33,1:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.67,1:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 你去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.54,1:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 我不是有意的 菲尼克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.01,1:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我害怕...很多事情
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.65,1:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 我恐高 我从没跟你说我害怕...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.42,1:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.60,1:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它在越变越大
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.54,1:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不肯消失
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.95,1:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.62,1:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问谁是菲尼克斯吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.99,1:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从没这样深的爱过
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.63,1:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从没这样爱过
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.30,1:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说明早7点半来我那里
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.94,1:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 他妈的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.35,1:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能怎么办? 再也不和人相爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.94,1:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你以为的那么简单
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.01,1:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.98,1:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.85,1:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么瘫痪的?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.65,1:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我5岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.62,1:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一个巴哈马岛的女人来到我们镇
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.42,1:07:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,携带了小儿麻痹症病毒
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.59,1:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在…一个朋友家
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.03,1:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她的小孩和我幼儿园同班
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.53,1:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,班上有4个孩子感染了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.53,1:07:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我穿着万圣节装扮
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.44,1:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去玩"不给糖就捣蛋"游戏
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.27,1:07:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈摸了摸我的额头 把我放在床上
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.41,1:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,半夜的时候 我意识到除了胳膊和双手
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.55,1:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的全身都动不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.28,1:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我哭着叫我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.32,1:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"我不能动了 我不能动了"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.02,1:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我送到医院
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.72,1:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,据说我活不过24小时
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.79,1:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我战斗 活了下来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.43,1:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你有上铁肺? (人工协助呼吸舱)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.76,1:08:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.83,1:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我回到家的床上
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.00,1:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和班上同学 靠一个小小的...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.71,1:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,扩音器联系
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.74,1:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的小孩被要求探望我
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.41,1:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在说 "嗨"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.82,1:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就不知道说什么了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.08,1:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都害怕我了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.22,1:08:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还是如此
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我让人们怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.86,1:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一个坐轮椅的"女魔头"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.33,1:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也让人害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.60,1:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,学会好好利用它
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.40,1:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要所有人的爱和认同
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.54,1:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 你的机构…毫无用处
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.47,1:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法得到董事会重量人物的支持
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.91,1:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过了300个病人 我 1个医生
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.34,1:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那些从我们那儿赚走无数钱的人…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.05,1:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,时尚 摇滚 电影 房地产 都别指望了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.72,1:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,任何时候只要布鲁斯和我有异议
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.32,1:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他就提请董事会表决  - 而你就输掉
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.59,1:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法通过做爱建议
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.96,1:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,或任何只要不是百分百确定的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.03,1:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,科学上根本没有百分百的确定
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.13,1:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随便怎么说都行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.60,1:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别吼我说我什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.43,1:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你那边又他妈的做了什么? - 我不知道!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.53,1:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你的全美医学会呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.40,1:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,作为犹太人 你是不是总感到饥饿?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.94,1:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我不是犹太人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.54,1:09:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是德国人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.88,1:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家都以为你是犹太人 - 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.45,1:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在医学界吃得开
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.65,1:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整个念书期间你都在床上度过的?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.99,1:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,上大学之前我戴上了第一套脚架
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.56,1:10:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我能...走一点点
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.70,1:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不怎么能走了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.10,1:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为我没时间去练习
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.40,1:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须练习
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.80,1:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在 我认真的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.44,1:10:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.61,1:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄坏了我的马蒂斯唱片 (美国歌王)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.28,1:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能邀您跳这支舞吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.82,1:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你自找的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.20,1:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的拐杖
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.96,1:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,, ♪在看见你的一刻 ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.04,1:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 也许你觉得 ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.54,1:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chances Are" (Johnny Mathis)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.12,1:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己能行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.96,1:11:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢... - 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.89,1:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.15,1:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕留下他一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.82,1:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕解药不能及时到来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.92,1:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕我的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.29,1:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是个糟糕的领袖... - 还是糟糕的舞者 把我放回去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.12,1:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小儿麻痹症也是种病毒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.12,1:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没人得小儿麻痹症了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.65,1:12:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿? 我们在这儿一个半小时了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.06,1:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人是谁? 我们就像在他妈的地窖
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.99,1:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能这样对我们 他不能这样对我们后还逍遥法外
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.73,1:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们开始了吗? - 没有
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.43,1:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 幸好 嗨 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.94,1:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷 简直是坟墓
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.70,1:13:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不想在地表看到我们吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.87,1:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿? 我都是迟到一小时了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.67,1:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个半小时 - 别找我的茬 坏家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.14,1:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 汤米 你在哪儿? - 我去贝尔维尤市了 (华盛顿州城市)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.31,1:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让一个快要死的可怜孩子和他的妈妈团聚
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.12,1:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有15年没见了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.79,1:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他从没告诉她自己是同志
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.72,1:13:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想见她 好几周都不让她过来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.19,1:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他妈妈进去的时候他很生气
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.83,1:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太让人伤心了 当妈妈搂着她儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.53,1:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.94,1:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起迟到了 我是希拉姆·吉布勒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.87,1:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 请问你在饼干业有亲戚吗? (吉布勒是美国第二大饼干制造商)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.74,1:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的 我是汤米·波特赖特
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.28,1:13:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,内德·维克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.71,1:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·奈尔斯 我是主席
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.95,1:13:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,市长想让你们知道他有多重视
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.82,1:13:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们肯担起自己的责任 有多么的刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.66,1:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 谢谢?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.26,1:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,责任? 我们做的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.16,1:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你们该做的 现在我们需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.26,1:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 维克斯先生其实想说的是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.86,1:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快超负荷了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.56,1:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每天要接500通热线电话
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.50,1:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们提供的信息 说实话
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.70,1:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是由市政府提供却没有的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.84,1:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我们需要办公场所 我们只有一个小间
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.97,1:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,每天有超过100人打电话来或进进出出
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.54,1:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,加上别人不肯租房子给我们 真的很棘手
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.71,1:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为... - 哇噢 这是非法歧视啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.68,1:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我们身受其害 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.18,1:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吉布勒先生 歧视同性恋不算非法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.89,1:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等待见市长已经等了14个月
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.32,1:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花了一年时间才能和你见面
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.49,1:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而你迟到了一个半小时
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.60,1:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你有告诉市长一场流行病正在爆发吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.95,1:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁说的? - 政府
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.20,1:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个政府? 我们的政府?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.96,1:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 流行病? - 全国疾控中心宣布...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.30,1:14:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 17个月前了 - 你不可能不知道!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.33,1:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请控制一下你的歇斯底里等级吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.30,1:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.84,1:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约 旧金山 洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.14,1:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,芝加哥 波士顿 丹佛 美国每一个主要城市
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.08,1:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都出现了病例
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.61,1:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有至少25个海外国家 可纽约市
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.42,1:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的家 你们宣称要保护的城市
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.92,1:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,占了大半数据
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.42,1:15:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大半发病率 大半死亡人数
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.22,1:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,57个我知道的已经死了 我不想再听到更多
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.99,1:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们什么时候能见市长?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.96,1:15:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,出去吃14个月的午饭已经够长了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.06,1:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你等一等 - 不 你可以等 我们不能
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.20,1:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不站在我们这边
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.10,1:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不肯向市长传话 我们能怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.20,1:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,买一个精壮男妓送到市长官邸
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.77,1:15:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在阴茎上刺上请愿的刺青吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.64,1:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 科奇市长不是同志! - 得了吧 "布兰奇" ("欲望号街车"女主角)
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.48,1:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.11,1:15:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们觉得我不想帮你们?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.92,1:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我有朋友正因为这鬼病而死去
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.49,1:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,此时此刻 就躺在医院里
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.92,1:15:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但情况很微妙 你们看到了 情况很微妙
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.76,1:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,微妙什么! 纽约有一百万同志
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.13,1:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,加上你就是一百万零一个!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.93,1:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗? 西区一所学校的暖气炉着火了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.50,1:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我一天就接到了3000个电话
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.74,1:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,懂我的意思吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.61,1:16:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们有很多人都很愤懑 为什么只有这个大嘴巴在滔滔不绝?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.91,1:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是个非常好的问题 - 好吧 假设本市有50万男同志
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.48,1:16:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,315个病人的比例也不算太高
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.32,1:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,相较于我们...你们的总人数
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.72,1:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是鬼扯! - 内德 求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.09,1:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道情况很微妙 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.99,1:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我们需要你的帮助 - 我认为 市长也认为
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.46,1:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们反应过度了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.16,1:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟那个吸鸡巴的说 他是个自私的 冷血的狗娘养的!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.37,1:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是迈克尔·马科斯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.34,1:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在市卫生署的职位就快要不保了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.67,1:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是你 就会管住你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.09,1:16:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信刚才发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.39,1:16:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇 我明天就上"今日秀"
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.03,1:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.59,1:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,市长用你的饭碗作要挟 要我们闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.30,1:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"今日秀"? 你要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.43,1:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我们当成狗屎 我们还由他们这样
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.47,1:17:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这些政客只会对压力做出回应
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.97,1:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到他说的了吧 "3000个西区的电话"?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.97,1:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫得还不够大声!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.85,1:17:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.32,1:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.74,1:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 汤米 - 汤米 我是内德
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.77,1:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 尼克死了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.51,1:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.78,1:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.78,1:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚点再告诉你纪念仪式的安排
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.02,1:18:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个传统
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.73,1:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当我认识的朋友死后我会做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.97,1:18:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他的名片保留下来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.37,1:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不然怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.07,1:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,扔进垃圾桶吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.17,1:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会那样做
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.01,1:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.88,1:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那太决绝
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.28,1:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去年我保留了5张名片
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.72,1:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我有50张了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.62,1:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,像一个纸片做的墓碑展览
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.36,1:18:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,用橡皮筋捆在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.36,1:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨死这些葬礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的恨
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.20,1:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我还恨什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.87,1:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨悼念仪式
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.97,1:18:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都变成我们的社交生活了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.34,1:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,参加这些活动
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.51,1:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克是个编舞师
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.65,1:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不晓得你们知不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.72,1:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他的事业刚起步 他没告诉过很多人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.02,1:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他期待着有一天
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.09,1:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,能邀请你们观看他在卡内基的盛大首场秀 (纽约著名音乐厅)
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.43,1:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会为他无比骄傲
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.97,1:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么优秀
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.30,1:19:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,前途那么光明
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.08,1:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在失去整整一代人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.45,1:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.62,1:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么走了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.05,1:19:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,编舞师 剧作家
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.89,1:19:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舞者 演员
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.29,1:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这些剧本再也不会完成了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.96,1:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这些舞蹈再也不会被跳了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.07,1:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,最后 我只想说我在狂怒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.64,1:20:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的狂怒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.18,1:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里不断尖叫 "为什么他们任我们死去?"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.42,1:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"为什么没人肯帮我们?"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.92,1:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而事实就是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.46,1:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,答案就是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.63,1:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是不喜欢我们
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.07,1:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要战胜这个
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.44,1:21:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都很幸运
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.61,1:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 这种态度就对了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.95,1:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在"时报"找工作 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.52,1:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要内德
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.56,1:22:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我有过给内德吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.20,1:22:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.00,1:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人感冒了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.34,1:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他的伴侣有时候会感染 有时不会
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.28,1:22:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有医生说用安全套就不会有事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.05,1:22:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.16,1:22:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们还能接吻吗? - 菲尼克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.23,1:22:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有作战的武器
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.93,1:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说你没有免疫系统
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.63,1:22:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体现在对各种可能的感染开放
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.67,1:22:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须谨慎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.17,1:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽我最大的努力 你也要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.24,1:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说你对所有男孩都这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.08,1:22:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.51,1:23:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.10,1:23:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 上帝
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很早很早以前 有个小男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.82,1:23:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一心想爱上另一个小男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.36,1:23:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天他终于找到了他的爱
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.49,1:23:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那种感觉好极了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.06,1:23:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我该戴上手套
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.56,1:23:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我该做这个 我该做那个
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.00,1:23:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该亲吻他
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.13,1:23:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 - 不该只是一个45岁的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.37,1:24:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾一个35岁的年轻男人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.34,1:24:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他看着像有100岁 而且快死了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.05,1:24:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛说这就是跷跷板
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.22,1:24:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿好 一会儿坏
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.79,1:24:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好些了…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.46,1:24:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又变得更糟
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.36,1:24:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝 救救我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.47,1:24:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他害怕我离开他
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.98,1:24:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他我不会离开他
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.78,1:24:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我一秒钟都没想过要离开他
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.12,1:24:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可他不相信我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.39,1:24:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个年代很难相信了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.06,1:24:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们必须永远不要停止相信彼此
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.80,1:25:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我一团糟 这就是我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.27,1:25:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你哭啊哭 觉得已经哭不出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.34,1:25:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你又哭出更多
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.62,1:25:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不只为自己或菲尼克斯 而是为所有小男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.39,1:25:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些终于找到了其他小男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.26,1:25:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这辈子期望的 而且变成了男人
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.67,1:25:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,男同志健康危机组织
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.94,1:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是埃斯特拉 能为你做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.70,1:25:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有人需要立遗嘱!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.54,1:25:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 内德在哪儿? 我要和他说话 - 他在里面
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.51,1:25:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给他这个号码 - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.91,1:25:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 男同志健康危机组织 - 男同志健康危机组织
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.24,1:25:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 我想我找到了4个合格的义务社工
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.15,1:25:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 全是拉拉 - 谢天谢地谢拉拉
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.28,1:25:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你直肠?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.52,1:25:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天王星啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.39,1:26:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢分享
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.06,1:26:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇 你为什么不在里约热内卢?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.29,1:26:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我把电话设成自动接听了 大家该休息一会儿了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.03,1:26:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想大家透支
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.50,1:26:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 菲尔 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.83,1:26:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.17,1:26:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜 宝贝 - 晚安 甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.34,1:26:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天工作很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.57,1:26:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.48,1:26:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔今天确诊了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.08,1:26:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇 为什么你不在里约热内卢度假?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.65,1:26:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来在 格里高利...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.79,1:26:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起在里约
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.96,1:26:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我接到了希拉姆从办公室打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.99,1:26:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说我今天一大早该去他的办公室
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.19,1:26:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从里约赶回来? 什么样的见面?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.16,1:26:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了市政厅 希勒姆让我一直等
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.17,1:26:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一个官员出来对我说
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.07,1:26:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉姆不愿意见我了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.44,1:27:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想大吼 "我两天都没睡觉 混球白痴"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.25,1:27:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没有 我说
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.22,1:27:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"那么请问 先生...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.25,1:27:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他大老远让我从里约赶回来?"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.32,1:27:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 "恐怕他不便向我透露了"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.99,1:27:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他就走了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.93,1:27:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,内德攻击希拉姆的文章刚发表了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.53,1:27:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想因为内德的自憎丢掉我的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.17,1:27:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么 米克?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.94,1:27:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你逼我们说一些我们不想说的话
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.94,1:27:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没法承担在交到足够朋友前
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.55,1:27:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,树立太多的敌人
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.95,1:27:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,特里·斯保丁从氧气舱里
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.75,1:27:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他的所有朋友打电话告别
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.32,1:27:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂比·毛瑞尔服药过量死
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.65,1:27:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔·谢克特的双脚现在假肢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.72,1:27:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗兰尼·桑图萨已经疯了! - 你能停停吗 停一停!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.63,1:27:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 米奇 你没事吧? - 我不觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.27,1:27:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么人们找不到病毒?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.67,1:27:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 那个需要时间
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.54,1:28:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我整天为市政做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.84,1:28:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是对比母乳喂养与婴儿食品
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.68,1:28:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,得了疱疹要如何保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.51,1:28:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上我会给我们的"本土人"写简报和健康专栏
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.65,1:28:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的…真的受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.05,1:28:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我写到了每一种理论
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.92,1:28:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,病毒的反复感染
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.92,1:28:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,休眠病毒的新形态
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.69,1:28:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,单病毒 新病毒 老病毒 多病毒 部分病毒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.23,1:28:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 潜伏病毒 变异病毒... - 放轻松 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.73,1:28:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定不要忘了做爱 吹箫
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.40,1:28:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻 血液 巫毒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.97,1:28:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,毒品 大麻 针头
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.74,1:28:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲 海地 古巴 黑人
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.01,1:28:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,变形虫 猪 还有他妈的天王星!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.98,1:28:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 假如这些都不是原因呢? - 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.42,1:28:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦大瘟疫 起源于一口水泵
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.52,1:28:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人...没有人注意到它
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.56,1:28:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是注定 或者是羊群理论...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.43,1:29:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只有很多人感染了 死够了才算完
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.90,1:29:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,万一是单一配偶的问题呢? 布鲁斯 你和我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.33,1:29:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至可能更糟
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.67,1:29:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为会被单一来源狂轰滥炸…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.31,1:29:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来自我们的爱人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.21,1:29:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也许那些去浴室的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.81,1:29:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们建立了最好的免疫系统
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.51,1:29:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么回答每个人 每个人都在问我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.91,1:29:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是对的? 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.48,1:29:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是错的? 我感觉...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.42,1:29:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉他妈的无助死了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.12,1:29:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎样对人们说 "停止"?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.26,1:29:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不…它可能是因为...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.13,1:29:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.70,1:29:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.53,1:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他是对的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.87,1:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而这更让我害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.47,1:29:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 你让我害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.84,1:29:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得总统...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.24,1:29:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望这一切发生? 你真的相信中情局
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.18,1:29:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,发动了细菌战
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.11,1:29:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来杀死杰瑞·法威尔厌恶的所有玻璃? (极端右翼政客)
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.11,1:29:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 米奇 冷静下来 - 怎么冷静?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.48,1:29:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经爱我的国家
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.39,1:30:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"本土人"杂志收到一封匿名信
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.39,1:30:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,说国防部在马里兰州的迪特里克堡进行一项绝密实验…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.79,1:30:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,生产了一种能破坏免疫系统的病毒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.49,1:30:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,代号是"强硬之手"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.63,1:30:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从1978年开始在一群同志身上做实验
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.63,1:30:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不相信这些的...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.97,1:30:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想迫害死我们!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.94,1:30:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会取消我们的医疗保险
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.77,1:30:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们关进集中营 隔离起来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.47,1:30:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是凶手吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.34,1:30:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没那么说 - 你心里清楚你是这么想
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.71,1:30:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子花了15年
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.75,1:30:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们的权利而战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.55,1:30:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我们自由的做爱 无论时间和地点
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.52,1:30:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你跟我说 我这么多年的努力
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.05,1:30:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些作为同志所代表的都是错误!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.06,1:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我成了凶手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.76,1:30:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经那么灰暗 你忘了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.10,1:30:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能看到这有多重要吗 我们能够公开的相爱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.24,1:30:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要躲藏 不需要负罪?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.34,1:30:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不能看到?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.45,1:31:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我去过帝国大厦顶层
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.64,1:31:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.03,1:31:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以从那儿跳下去 没人管你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.75,1:31:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 米奇 我们回家 现在就回家
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.83,1:31:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,内德 我不是凶手 我不是
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.10,1:31:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都被人恨 因为是同志
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.86,1:31:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为个子矮
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.63,1:31:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是犹太人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.30,1:31:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你跟别人说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.87,1:31:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟所有人说我们错了 我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.04,1:31:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天 总有个人会出现
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.57,1:31:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他会狠狠捅你一刀
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.38,1:31:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说 你这辈子付出的一切 你的一生都是浪费!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.61,1:31:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.78,1:31:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇!住手!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.52,1:31:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手  来这儿 – 没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.19,1:31:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.35,1:31:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在送你回家 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.49,1:31:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想回家 送我去圣文森医院
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.56,1:31:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来吧 我们走
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.67,1:31:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 我们都很累了 听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.84,1:32:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这儿的负能量都快爆表了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.88,1:32:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是战士 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.78,1:32:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们是… - 当然是 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.42,1:32:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你是英雄 听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.22,1:32:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你知不知道 你都是个英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.16,1:32:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们的第一个英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.16,1:32:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.54,1:32:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做主席吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.54,1:32:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想菲尼克斯活下来
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.82,1:32:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,男同健康危机组织
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.29,1:32:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,海勒姆 老伙计 还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.60,1:33:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.57,1:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了? - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.14,1:33:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,市长找到一笔小的秘密资金
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.11,1:33:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以秘密的拨给我们
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.48,1:33:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能告诉任何人钱从哪儿来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.88,1:33:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们说了 就再也不会有
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.98,1:33:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 多少? - 9千块
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.49,1:33:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,内德
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.09,1:33:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔伯特死了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.06,1:33:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈妈想在他死前 在凤凰城见他最后一面
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.47,1:33:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显他只剩最后一周了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.74,1:33:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到了艾玛的许可证明 带他去机场
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.88,1:33:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们上了飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.79,1:34:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,机长拒绝驾驶
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.92,1:34:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而我拒绝下飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.09,1:34:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在的话肯定会为我骄傲 内德
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.90,1:34:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最后终于换了一个机长
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.50,1:34:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当飞机起飞后
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.50,1:34:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔伯特开始失控了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.84,1:34:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想呆在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.21,1:34:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事 – 我不想呆在这地方…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.58,1:34:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要下去 – 别 埃尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.48,1:34:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.35,1:34:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 埃尔伯特 – 让他坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.85,1:34:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不好意思 – 先生 先生 你得坐好
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.79,1:34:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快坐下 - 先生 请你坐下 你得…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.23,1:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.53,1:34:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生… - 停下!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.70,1:34:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,先生!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.40,1:34:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们坐下 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.90,1:34:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他认不出我了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.37,1:34:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.87,1:34:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道我们要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.98,1:34:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们就快到了 – 不知道我们要去凤凰城
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.14,1:35:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,见他妈妈… 什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.11,1:35:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他变得….
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.98,1:35:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼 能给一我条毛巾吗 谢谢?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.15,1:35:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到达凤凰城 等我们到医院
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.36,1:35:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他母亲已经把房间收拾得很好…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.46,1:35:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔伯特已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.14,1:35:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,医院的医生不愿给他尸检
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.91,1:35:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的死亡证明上开具死亡原因
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.51,1:35:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而没有死亡证明 殡仪馆就不肯收他
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.21,1:35:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 警察也不管 – 哥们 拖它下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.95,1:35:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,终于一个护理员进来 把我的埃尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.82,1:35:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,塞进一个大号的垃圾袋
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.29,1:35:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把他和其他垃圾一起丢进巷子里的垃圾堆
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.89,1:35:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮了你一个大忙 我把他弄了出来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.03,1:35:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要50块
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.39,1:36:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是全部的骨灰? - 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.66,1:36:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要? 3千块
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.37,1:36:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了 走了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.17,1:36:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.78,1:36:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.95,1:36:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你们说 他们在谋杀我们
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.12,1:36:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们让他们这样
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.55,1:36:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.25,1:36:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.99,1:36:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们都他妈的站起来还击
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.54,1:37:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛在那儿等着
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.32,1:37:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来 就两口 来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.29,1:37:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 不  – 别让我拿酸奶出气
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.17,1:37:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再一口 – 你跟你哥哥和好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.14,1:37:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你的这个样子
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.85,1:37:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不跟这个世界上你最爱的人说话
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.89,1:38:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我好起来 但我好不起来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.46,1:38:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到特别他妈的内疚
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.44,1:38:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你周五跟比尔·布拉斯有个午餐预约
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.61,1:38:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 高档啊 – 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.95,1:38:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我会打给他致歉
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.78,1:38:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.25,1:38:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你订一个两月后的约会
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.85,1:38:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我被邀请去耶鲁的同志一周演讲
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.36,1:38:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会一起去 记得我跟你说过现在他们的那些舞会吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.99,1:38:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的舞伴
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.79,1:39:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我太想要你活下来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.36,1:39:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我不该说出来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.47,1:39:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 求你再给我们一年
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.24,1:39:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证会吃菠菜
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.34,1:40:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我医治的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.00,1:40:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个疾病的患者数量
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.97,1:40:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,超过世界上所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.61,1:40:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我有更多冷藏血样
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.78,1:40:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,更多各种数据
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.91,1:40:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和更多经验
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.12,1:40:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁克娜医生 政府的立场是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.62,1:40:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在5千5百万拨款项目中
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.46,1:40:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有5百万准备发放
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.09,1:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,5百万对2000起病例来说并不怎么多
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.86,1:40:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,光7个泰伦诺死亡的案例 政府就花了3百万来调查 (一种镇痛药)
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.80,1:40:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经进入第三年了 – 我们投票驳回
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.60,1:40:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的资金申请
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.07,1:40:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.54,1:40:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听你们的理由
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.01,1:40:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你建议的研究方向
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.25,1:40:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不精确也没有重点
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.11,1:40:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这样啊 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.68,1:40:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你对正发生的完全不比我知道得更多
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.95,1:40:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我究竟是为什么要阻碍我的研究?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.46,1:40:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁克娜医生 还有其他的研究员
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.13,1:41:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经不是你一个人的疾病了 尽管你这么认为
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.36,1:41:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我是这么想的啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.80,1:41:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是来把它从我这儿拿走 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.60,1:41:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你一个小秘密 医生
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.27,1:41:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拿走 我一开始就不想要它
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.04,1:41:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得看着年轻人去死是一种殊荣?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.47,1:41:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我干嘛跟你争辩?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.48,1:41:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你连蒸馏水都不知道是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.74,1:41:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么资格过来对我评头论足?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.01,1:41:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是应莫里医生请求来进行业内小组评估
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.98,1:41:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,又一个白痴 顺便说 还是深柜的同性恋
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.92,1:41:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,竭尽他的所能把这一切扫进地毯下面
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.12,1:41:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我还发过誓永远不在公众场合说这些
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.43,1:41:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么总是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.03,1:41:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,总是白痴在这样的小组里面?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.43,1:41:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么能驳回我的研究资金申请
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.83,1:41:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或者不邀请我参加你们的?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.04,1:41:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的国家卫生研究所
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.37,1:41:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,两年前就收到了我的第一份资金申请
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.54,1:41:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们花了一年时间把申请表打印出来
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.08,1:41:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,从我第一个上报案例算起 你们花了三年时间
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.88,1:42:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这里看一眼 而微不足道的那一点钱
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.79,1:42:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们逼我们去乞讨
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.19,1:42:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,从你们每年收到的40亿经费里面
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.09,1:42:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,施舍一点来捍卫美国人民的健康
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.86,1:42:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且天知道它们时候到位
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.76,1:42:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,法国已经发现了一种有可能相关的病毒
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.63,1:42:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么拒绝跟法国人合作?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.40,1:42:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们被告诫不得和法国人合作?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.11,1:42:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就为你们可以偷到诺贝尔奖
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.44,1:42:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就让这种疾病流行 导致死亡吗!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.08,1:42:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲已经发现了女性病例
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.48,1:42:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显这种病会在异性恋中传播
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.32,1:42:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.15,1:42:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们做点什么之前我们可能都已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.66,1:42:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我的数据? 我的构想?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.23,1:42:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的病人? 拿去!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.13,1:42:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只求你能做点什么!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.84,1:42:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你说对了! 我是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.67,1:42:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不精确也没有重点 而你们是白痴!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.05,1:43:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你组织的对市长的抗议?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.09,1:43:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.04,1:43:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有标语?- 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.26,1:43:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的下一部戏据说是关于第一夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.80,1:43:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在好莱坞得到最好的口交 – 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.50,1:43:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里做我们的新办公室再合适不过 – 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.88,1:43:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好干净
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.88,1:43:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.78,1:43:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.52,1:43:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来 送你去床上躺躺
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.19,1:43:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.89,1:43:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.82,1:43:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯特拉给你做了些等会儿吃的白菜卷
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.50,1:43:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎已经有一种新药
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.73,1:44:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒的爱人飞去取了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.27,1:44:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 HPA-23
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.61,1:44:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,内德
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.85,1:44:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他情况很糟 – 你觉得这个真的有用吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.55,1:44:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还是跟其他药一样的没用?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.66,1:44:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你得做好心理准备放手了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.30,1:44:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能为自己爱的人放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.90,1:44:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没有为自己爱的人而战过吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.41,1:44:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 你得试着站出来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.78,1:44:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样别人才能看到我所看到的你
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.42,1:44:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么狗屁做爱戏啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.57,1:45:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.80,1:45:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 女士?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.41,1:45:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明天4点半?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.41,1:45:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 女士
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.81,1:45:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的白宫打来的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.15,1:45:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的市长 我刚被邀请去白宫了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.32,1:45:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要行动了!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.16,1:45:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想搞清楚一下
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.63,1:45:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的这个头衔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.43,1:45:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟可以对我们的瘟疫做些什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.83,1:45:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不使用消极编制 那样只会吓到民众
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.03,1:45:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有3,339个病例了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.74,1:45:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,1,122人死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.54,1:45:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说这就是瘟疫 我被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.68,1:45:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.58,1:45:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你的头衔是什么意思来着?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.41,1:45:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我给总统提供建议
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.71,1:45:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,关于该做什么 不该做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.65,1:46:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 收到
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.32,1:46:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 拨款还有对吧? 没有被花掉
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.12,1:46:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在法国有一种新药
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.22,1:46:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么国家卫生所不研究它?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.86,1:46:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我想要的 我们想要的 我们亟需要的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.43,1:46:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是有人帮助我们删减这些官样文章
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.76,1:46:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 我的每一周
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.10,1:46:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有不向总统提供新信息和汇报情况的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.07,1:46:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个病的进展已经很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.60,1:46:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可它会传染
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.81,1:46:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看到就因为它会传染
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.64,1:46:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得…得尽快行动吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.41,1:46:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得任何人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.28,1:46:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个国家的公共政策人员心里面
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.42,1:46:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是它们最闭门的会议上
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.65,1:46:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会对彼此说  "嘿 各位
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.45,1:46:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是别为这事太烦恼好吗?"
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.49,1:46:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你的老板现在还没大声说过"艾滋"这个词
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.47,1:47:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.61,1:47:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个病... 妓女可能得这个病吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.71,1:47:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,或者 一夜情的人?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.08,1:47:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然 – 你不能证明
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.82,1:47:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 从我了解到的和读到的来看
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.02,1:47:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,男女性通过一般阴道交媾
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.05,1:47:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而传播的效率并不怎么高
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.56,1:47:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这么简单 它是病毒 病毒不会歧视
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.26,1:47:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.96,1:47:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,传播起来很难 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.70,1:47:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对一个直人来说
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.43,1:47:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一个普通异性恋男子来说几乎是不可能的 我说得对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.24,1:47:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 还没有登记的病例 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.04,1:47:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一起登记的病例
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.14,1:47:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,证明异性恋男子会得这个
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.98,1:47:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,无论通过做爱或是口交?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.28,1:47:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有这方面的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.45,1:47:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.73,1:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊 准备我的会议
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.46,1:48:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会晚到15分钟 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.31,1:48:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 非常感谢你 –  等等
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.17,1:48:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 随时联系 – 先生 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.55,1:48:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,预计会有1亿人感染
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.99,1:48:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是没有人重视!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.69,1:48:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,2楼需要保安
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.12,1:48:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛坐在地上?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.76,1:49:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我摔倒了 在从这头到那头的途中
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.43,1:49:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我 我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.34,1:49:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌你那样看着我
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.01,1:49:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了吗? 我饿了 你呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.31,1:49:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了我约会簿里的所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.35,1:49:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其他和我睡过的人都没得病
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.49,1:49:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你才是携带者
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.56,1:49:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要这样对彼此
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.30,1:49:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯 你会好起来 你会的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.50,1:49:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛说国家卫生所终于开始研究了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.24,1:49:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们得抱着希望 – 噢 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.98,1:49:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 – 是吗? 我能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.32,1:50:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别吃那些垃圾食品!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.45,1:50:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我 – 不!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.89,1:50:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道保持营养的重要性
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.99,1:50:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寿命预期只有10分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.99,1:50:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃什么就吃什么
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.34,1:50:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,内德
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.81,1:50:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我越来越差了 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.31,1:50:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你看着我死
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.15,1:50:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能逼我做任何事
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.45,1:50:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你该比其他人都更知道这个
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.12,1:50:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备剩下的日子都坐在那个地板上吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.52,1:50:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听到我说的了吗? - 你听到我说的了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.92,1:50:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有! - 没有?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.55,1:50:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经接受超过40种治疗 没有?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.76,1:50:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了3种…不 4种不同化疗 没有!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.63,1:50:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过3种实验药
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.20,1:50:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛花在我身上的时间比任何人都多
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.83,1:50:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可什么用也没有!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.84,1:50:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你总不能强迫太阳出来!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.60,1:51:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了那些争吵
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.44,1:51:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.64,1:51:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,盲目还有负罪感之旅
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.51,1:51:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西你不吃? 那就别吃了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.28,1:51:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管了 吃你的毒药 我不管了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.12,1:51:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼对你身体有益
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.72,1:51:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不想吃 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.39,1:51:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,绿色莎拉也不要了!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.66,1:51:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,西兰花不要了! 蔬菜不要了!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.43,1:51:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,带7种谷物的面包也不要了!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.83,1:51:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有人想喝牛奶呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.00,1:51:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你骨头里面有钙了!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.87,1:51:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你想死吗 菲尼克斯?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.17,1:51:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.60,1:51:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 别离开我 菲尼克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.71,1:52:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.74,1:52:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.34,1:52:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.01,1:52:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.68,1:52:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.45,1:52:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.98,1:52:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.62,1:52:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.19,1:52:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.75,1:52:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.42,1:52:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.86,1:52:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.53,1:52:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.96,1:52:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.59,1:52:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.96,1:52:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,走开! 走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.46,1:52:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.00,1:52:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,混球些
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.50,1:52:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,男同健康危机组织
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.44,1:52:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,鹅口疮是种真菌 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.00,1:52:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他我们会在那儿抗议
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.50,1:52:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不怕逮捕或警察暴力
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.04,1:52:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 男同健康危机组织 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.21,1:52:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,市长还有4小时
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.58,1:52:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不见我们 我们就行使非暴力不合作
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.98,1:52:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米昨天收到电话了 内德
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.79,1:52:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不告诉我?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.05,1:52:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 我说了能行!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.79,1:53:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候? 什么时候? - 只有两个人可以去见市长 内德
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.86,1:53:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候? - 汤米是执行董事
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.73,1:53:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.90,1:53:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会提董事会投票 内德  – 我写给市长的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.93,1:53:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那封信 那个会面是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.97,1:53:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要代表这个组织去那儿
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.84,1:53:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我把生命的每分钟都花在为它战斗上面
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.51,1:53:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的客厅成立的组织
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.48,1:53:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就不干了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.38,1:53:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我不干?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.56,1:53:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,董事会要我大声对你念这个
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.36,1:53:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 念什么? - 这封信
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.61,1:53:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你读啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.88,1:53:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经广泛传阅这封信
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.11,1:54:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在有判断力和良好认知的人当中
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.58,1:54:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须制止你庞大的个人主义膨胀
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.32,1:54:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,反复一而再的玩弄恐惧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.29,1:54:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 是完全粗暴的行径
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.13,1:54:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,将同志的死加以占用
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.80,1:54:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在全美的电视和出版物上兜售
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.20,1:54:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 是一种破坏
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.77,1:54:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而在性解放多年后
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.14,1:54:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我们再对性感到肮脏…
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.74,1:54:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕和成为禁忌
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.31,1:54:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对你的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.12,1:54:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,超过我们对生命中的任何人
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.29,1:54:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们觉得你想要领导我们
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.02,1:54:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.82,1:54:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想要你来领导
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.70,1:54:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,根据由威克斯 弗兰克尔 莱温施泰起草的章程
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.14,1:55:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,内德先生将被免除
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.74,1:55:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,男同健康危机组织的董事职务
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.54,1:55:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们乞求你安静的离开我们
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.58,1:55:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别毁掉我们和我们从事的美好事业
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.72,1:55:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你赞不赞成
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.35,1:55:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,立即生效
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.61,1:55:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,内德
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.11,1:55:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,执行董事不在董事会里 你知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.38,1:55:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有投票权
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.02,1:55:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.49,1:55:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没支持我 – 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.89,1:55:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都在从事殡仪业
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.32,1:55:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,整个组织就是个殡仪馆
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.06,1:55:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 内德… - 你们做的全部就是照顾死者
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.83,1:56:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来为活着的人战斗 好让他们继续活着?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.10,1:56:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来为我的菲尼克斯战斗?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.20,1:56:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 我们需要你去楼上
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.41,1:56:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我属于的地方 有马塞尔·普鲁斯特
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.21,1:56:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔特·惠特曼 田纳西·威廉斯 亚历山大大帝 (均为同性恋名人)
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.61,1:56:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多你不敢相信的教皇和主教
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.45,1:56:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,特种部队先生 你知道是一个公开出柜的英国同志
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.52,1:56:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,令第二次世界大战获胜的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.15,1:56:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字叫艾伦·图灵 他破解了恩尼格玛
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.76,1:56:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,战争结束后他自杀了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.66,1:56:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他为是同志饱受折磨
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.66,1:56:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他们从来不在学校里教这些?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.33,1:56:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一个同志我们才取得二战的胜利!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.00,1:56:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们这样做了 也许他就不会自杀
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.77,1:56:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会这么害怕做真实的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.41,1:56:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我希望被人记住的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.45,1:56:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个赢得了战争的人
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.45,1:57:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯 我知道我是个混球
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.56,1:57:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但请不要把我拒之门外
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.63,1:57:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.95,1:58:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟和我是恋人
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.88,1:58:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了 我想立一份遗嘱
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.12,1:58:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请坐 – 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.64,1:58:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把所有东西都留给内德
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.64,1:58:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我弟弟还好吗? – 他把所有事都怪在自己头上
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.98,1:58:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,从我要死了 到整个世界的局势
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.99,1:58:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这些 加上你们仍然不讲话
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.86,1:58:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定跟他一样倔
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.43,1:58:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快打给他
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.13,1:58:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在 他正在家收拾行李
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.30,1:58:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去耶鲁几天
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.87,1:59:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,参加同志一周
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.97,1:59:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他都不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.98,1:59:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那儿读大一时差点自杀
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.92,1:59:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我没多少留下...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.26,1:59:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,除了一块漂亮的地
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.86,1:59:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在威尔佛力特的海角 (马萨诸塞州)
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.10,1:59:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,内德不知道这个
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.66,1:59:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,本来想作为惊喜给他的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.60,1:59:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们去那儿定居
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.94,1:59:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,从此快乐的生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.14,1:59:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一张保单
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.54,1:59:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,跟”时报”签的 我是记者...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.85,1:59:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约时报的记者
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.58,1:59:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,该留给我的最近亲人的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.45,1:59:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕他们不会给他
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.09,1:59:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他被列为受益人 他们必须给他
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.22,1:59:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个世界怎样 别这么天真
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.66,1:59:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 我会尽我的一切保证它履行
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.63,2:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等你这句话
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.27,2:00:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尼克斯…
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.11,2:00:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能早认识你就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.68,2:01:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该穿白色的衣服
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.78,2:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是穿的白色衣服 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.77,2:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,应该…应该是
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.81,2:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,派瑞·艾力斯为我个人定制的 (美国著名男装设计师)
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.09,2:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,内德?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.73,2:01:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要想办法再次战斗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.40,2:01:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.14,2:01:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.47,2:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.89,2:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 艾玛…
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.65,2:02:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们… 我们能开始了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.43,2:02:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿 在上帝的注视下
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.34,2:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为这两位男士结合作证
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.54,2:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们爱对方
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.77,2:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,非常的深 而且…
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.98,2:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,希望在他们的家人面前 朋友面前 结合
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.25,2:02:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到异议
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.59,2:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你 菲尼克斯·特勒
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.82,2:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 接受内德·威克斯… – 我的亚历山大 我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.46,2:02:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 成为你的... – 我最好 最真的爱
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.47,2:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.98,2:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意 我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.88,2:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.85,2:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.46,2:03:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意 我愿意
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.89,2:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是汤米
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.56,2:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢跟我说
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.07,2:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Only Living Boy In New York” (Simon & Garfunkel)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Please prepare to exit the ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:44.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Man: Attention on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are now arriving at Fire Island Pines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome to Fire Island, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Please take care exiting the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Those steps can be wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Also double-check you have all your luggage...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:02.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hey, Weeks. - Hey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hairy is out. Your turn, teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I love my teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:50.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Calvin Klein would not approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Baseball game is on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and my summer has officially begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The thing is, he actually means it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hey, baby. - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Cold beer? - No, I've already had a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice stripes, Lieutenant. Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, please... Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Just got back from the Reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:11.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what they say, once a month I get to play a real man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, haven't seen you at the gym lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Your turn, Bruce. - What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:21.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Brucey, please, don't embarrass our house at the beach, hon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. Gotta do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what they say, Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If you can't beat 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,join 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's my guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Craig was miserable when you weren't interested
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now look. He's got Robert Redford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Shows you there is a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- How's John? - John?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- John. - John? Oh, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I'm with Gregory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're celebrating our 15-month anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,15? That's a long time for you, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, please, we're lovers and we live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not like we're faithful to each other, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:09.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's not even Jewish. Don't tell my rabbi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:17.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey,Bruce you suck
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you even come here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You made us look terrible in your novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look around you. Sex is liberating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All I said was having so much sex makes finding love impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do not put your failure to find someone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- on the rest of us. - Neddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ow! - Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You okay? - I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Just got a little lightheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I got myself up. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just got a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He seemed okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:19.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,? Happy bdadaday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:25.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,? Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:31.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,? Happy birthday, dear Craig
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:37.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,? Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I fucking love this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:20.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned! Hey, Ned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I sold you a ceramic pig once
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,at Maison France on Bleecker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Sanford.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody I was friends with then collected pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and you had the biggest pig I'd ever seen outside a real pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They just keep getting bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm her 20th case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And six of them are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Ned. Won't be a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Buzzy. I didn't know you worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:17.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, Ned Weeks. I spoke to you after the "Times" article.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come in. Take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I only came to ask some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You are gay, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Take your clothes off. Don't be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've seen more men than you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,To answer all of your questions, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never seen or heard of anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you had any of the symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Most of the shit the "Times" said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,amoebas, gonorrhea, hepatitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't know what it's been like since the sexual revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What makes you think I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Any fever, night sweats, weight loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't I wish. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And purple lesions? Open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a strange reaction in the immune system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's collapsed. Won't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So the diseases most of my patients are coming down with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,are brought on by germs that wouldn't hurt a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tick wlish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,At least not a baby in New York City anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The immune system is the system we know the least about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So where's this big mouth I hear you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Is big mouth a symptom? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This seems to only be happening to gay men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Buzzy says you are well-known in the gay community
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and not afraid to say what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't find any gay leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I call gay organizations, no one ever calls me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Brookner, no one with half a brain gets involved with gay politics
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- There's no room for criticism. - What's your criticism?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate that we play victim
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,when many of us, most of us, don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Then you're exactly what's needed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe they're just waiting for someone to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want to lead them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What exactly are you trying to get me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell gay men to stop having sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you think that this cancer is sexually transmitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think it is, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I prove it yet? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you realize that you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,millions of men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,who have singled out promiscuity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,as their principal political agenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- How do you deal with that? - Tell them they may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where? - Down the hall. Down the hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not that simple. It's more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They think sex is all they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Weeks, if having sex can kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,doesn't anyone with half a brain stop fucking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can go. I'm not finding what I'm looking for here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where? - Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where? Where? - Right in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Just put him up on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Up here. Let's find a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Baby, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Be still. - Can you tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We were meeting him outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We turned the corner and he just collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, get the fuck out of the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Oh, my God! - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Who's the lover? - I am, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- What's your name? - Bruce Niles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Brookner. I need a room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Niles, you were Reinhardt's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He died three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Wouldn't even let me say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:22.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Not even let me kiss him goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It can happen this fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No one else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You make these assumptions on the basis of 46 cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You wanted to know what I think. This is what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You are all going to infect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:27.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now only a few of you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we can't tell yet which ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:34.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Long before we isolated the hepatitis viruses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,we knew about the diseases they caused
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and how they got around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where are the medical journals? The "Times"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I sent my first reports to the medical journals over a year ago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me, how do you know what you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,real quick, if you don't know what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I guess that's a dumb question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it isn't. It's the smartest question of all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and the hardest one to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't common sense tell you you should cool it for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That doesn't leave much to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What if it turns out that you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Let her speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The worst that could happen would be that you cooled it for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, excuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me. That is not the worst that will have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Guys will become frightened of sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We will lose our self-respect that we fought very, very hard for
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We will be scapegoated worse than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The world will think we're carriers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and the Moral Majority will have even more of a field day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am not coming back until this bitch on wheels is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait. I see more cases each week than the week before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Half of all my patients die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I hope she winds this up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,'cause I've got a tiny little orgy in New Rochelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where's the health department? Where's the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Shut the fuck up, John. - Oh, you shut the fuck up, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What are the numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Is every gay meeting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Half these people just showed up to get laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Quiet! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're starting a group. We're starting a health crisis group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're gonna meet here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Next time, bring some fucking food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey. That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome to gay politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm very late for an important meeting with Craig Claiborne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's expecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hi, Felix Turner. - And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:25.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My name's Ned Weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You caught me at a rough moment, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I have a deadline. The First Lady is coming to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been told you're gay and you might be able
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to help me get some vital information in the "Times."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You've "been told"? And who was it that told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, honey, everybody's talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why does everyone gay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,think that I run "The New York Times"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't help you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear that. What would you suggest I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Take your pick. I got 23 parties
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,37 new restaurants, 12 new discos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen, I can't get anyone here to write another article.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've talked to half a dozen reporters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and the guy who worked on the first piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"Mr. Leather"? Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No one here will write about it and I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, we're very compartmentalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want science to write about sweaters, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a very peculiar feeling having to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and seek support from a straight world for something gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just write about gay designers and gay discos
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and gay chefs and gay models and gay rock stars
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and gay celebrities and gay everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just don't call them gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't it time you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, I really do have a deadline
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't want me to get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Guys like you give me a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You in the book? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, guys. Give to gay cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, give to gay cancer? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi. Give to gay cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, give to gay cancer? There's a cancer in the gay community.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:08.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you give to gay cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a... there's a crisis in our community right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We could really use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We could use a little help. Anything? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you could be a little less aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Less aggressive? We've tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you give to cancer in our community?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, give to gay cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, give to gay cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:32.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's funny. My mother sent flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And I had never told her I was gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just told her that Craig had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:42.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:46.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think somehow mothers always know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:01.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't spending $5 million on a house frighten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Scared the shit out of me even having you handling my finances
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can have a house anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, your account needs more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not doing too badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I miss you being in the movie business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I like movies. - Do I detect a note of approval
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,from the big brother that called me "Lemon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Then why have you been searching in the country for so long for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- No fun living in it alone. - This Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is he someone you're seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I see him, he doesn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,could your law firm take this on for free
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What's it called? Pro bono?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We started an organization, I told you there's this new disease…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now this sounds like just another excuse to keep from writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why can't you just say "yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you because we have a committee that decides that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But you're the senior partner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I'm your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Mario. How's Homer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna help, I'm gonna have to find somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Well, you're more than free to do that. - I don't want to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want my big brother's fancy, famous, big-time, major law firm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:12.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to be the first straight New York law firm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to do pro bono work for a gay cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd be real proud of that and you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll ask my partners' approval at the next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll lobby them. You don't sound like a very sure vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're getting better at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm seeing three to four new patients a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:50.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got seven in ICU. The whole hospital only has room for 30
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've had to admit some of them under other illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got 20 in private rooms they can't afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, what about the guys who don't have health insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:01.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Artists, actors? - I've got eight of them in another ward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,where I shouldn't put them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you wear gloves and a face mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Never have and I never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:23.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is all the food sitting outside their rooms like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's getting cold. - It's always cold
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:27.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,because the appropriate staff won't bring it into the rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:31.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,so it sits and rots until one of my staff can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:35.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Right there. Yeah, by the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:36.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, right through the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.63,0:22:39.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Take the tunnel. We'll take the book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know him. Can I go inside with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Only if you wear all the protective shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:56.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Over there. Go the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me? Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hi, Sanford. - You see that? Take the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead, drive straight through.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:05.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How we doing, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:08.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want my dog. Can you please bring me my dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:10.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He won't be able to live without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want my dog. I want my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:15.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Good. No. Take the book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:20.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Right there. Pull hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you please bring me my dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He won't know how to live without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:36.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who's going to bring me my dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:39.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,His name is Skip. He'll come when you call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:59.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you imagine this at 19?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:02.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your first boyfriend you were gonna spend your whole life with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Excuse me. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:13.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the TV guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Please go to room 407 and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:18.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- No I'm not gonna do that. - Fix the TV. It's your fucking job
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:21.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My union says I don't gotta risk my life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:23.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,for some contagious fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:26.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If I have to go in there, then I fucking quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.31,0:24:38.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So what exactly has your side been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:05.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:08.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:09.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Want some of this? A beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:11.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, beer's fine. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:16.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, pooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.39,0:25:19.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Her name's Sam. - Hi, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:22.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, I really used to like high-tech
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,but I'm tired of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.63,0:25:27.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I want chintz back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.26,0:25:29.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:30.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.90,0:25:34.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want chintz back again, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:37.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:39.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Two fellows who want chintz back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.44,0:25:41.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess this really is a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:47.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:49.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You glad I'm here? - Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.49,0:25:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm pleased as punch you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.12,0:25:53.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're very good-looking. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:54.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You think you're bad-looking or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.89,0:25:57.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.19,0:25:59.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm from Oklahoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.83,0:26:02.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I left home at 18, put myself through...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:05.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,what, you wanna dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:08.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Put myself through college.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.30,0:26:11.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My dad worked at the refinery in West Tulsa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:13.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and my mom was a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:15.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Had a luncheonette in Walgreens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.98,0:26:20.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's amazing, isn't it? How a kid comes out of all that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.75,0:26:22.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and wind up on the "Times"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,dictating taste and style to the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.95,0:26:27.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And we were just starting to talk so nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.79,0:26:29.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Talking's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:31.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Shutting up's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.26,0:26:33.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you write all that fancy ball gown bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:36.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I bet you gobble it up every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.83,0:26:40.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know 10 people who have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.60,0:26:43.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,When I came to you, it was only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.27,0:26:46.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:48.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that why you agreed to this date?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.95,0:26:58.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Fork on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.85,0:27:00.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Knife on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.42,0:27:06.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you know that Hitler's Final Solution to eliminate the Polish Jews
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.96,0:27:09.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,was first mentioned in the "Times"? It was on page 28.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.30,0:27:11.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,On page 6 of the "Washington Post."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.30,0:27:14.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They are both owned by Jews. Their very own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.03,0:27:17.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Scholars are finally writing honestly about it and it's damning to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:20.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where is the Christian churches? The Pope? Churchill? Roosevelt?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.81,0:27:22.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,A few words from any of them would have put Hitler on notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.81,0:27:26.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dachau was open in 1933. Where the fuck was everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.95,0:27:31.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is turning out to be a very romantic evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:33.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You've never had a lover, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:35.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I suppose you've had quite a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:37.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I had a very good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.26,0:27:40.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,For a number of years, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.89,0:27:44.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He was older than I was and he found someone younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:49.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You looking for a father? - No, I'm not looking for a father. God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:50.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.54,0:28:01.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:02.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:05.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Everybody had a million reasons for not getting involved
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.52,0:28:08.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The American Jews knew exactly what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:11.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Could you imagine if every Jew had marched on Washington proudly?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.92,0:28:13.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:18.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't remember me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.26,0:28:20.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It was at the baths a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.93,0:28:25.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to Man's Country, see what we're all about
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.64,0:28:27.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and what we have to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.67,0:28:30.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Man's Country is a full facility, multileveled complex
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.71,0:28:33.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that was designed to feature something for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.94,0:28:36.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to Man's Country to develop your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.48,0:28:39.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,or a friendship with somebody else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:42.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Visit us once and you'll come again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.77,0:29:02.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You thought I was applying for the CIA the way you looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:05.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:13.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I followed you into your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.16,0:29:28.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You couldn't even open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:31.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You told me your real name was Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.44,0:29:38.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I asked what you did and you said something like
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.21,0:29:41.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,you "tried a number of things" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.58,0:29:43.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I asked if that had included love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:49.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's when you said, "I have to get up early in the morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:50.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:57.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Men do not naturally not love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.83,0:30:01.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They learn not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.80,0:30:07.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you're a bluffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:11.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How could I not remember you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.00,0:30:12.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:14.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It was very dark.
