Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:31.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Queen control.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.41,0:43:33.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Really works when it wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.16,0:43:45.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Felix. This is Dick Lombardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.43,0:43:46.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hi. - Finally got us someone on our board
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.93,0:43:48.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,who isn't a disco dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.56,0:43:50.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well... maybe tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.56,0:43:52.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'll see ya. - Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.53,0:43:54.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.61,0:44:10.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.48,0:44:40.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are all so happy you joined us tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.21,0:44:44.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are proving that we are more than just
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:47.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,looks, brains, talent and heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.49,0:44:51.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Together we raised more than any gay group ever in this city
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.93,0:44:56.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And I wanna call over
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.13,0:44:58.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Ned Weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.26,0:45:02.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.11,0:45:10.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.54,0:45:13.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We will now reveal just how much we raised together.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.74,0:45:15.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.95,0:45:18.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,$53,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.57,0:45:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Gay Men's Health Crisis, come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.44,0:45:40.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Felix, honey, come on up, please. Come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.54,0:45:42.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.78,0:45:47.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.30,0:46:19.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪Someday he'll come along♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.04,0:46:22.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ The man I love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.51,0:46:26.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And he'll be big and strong♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.41,0:46:30.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪The man I love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.12,0:46:33.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And when he comes my way♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.89,0:46:36.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ I'll do my best♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.22,0:46:43.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪To make him stay♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.40,0:46:49.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ He'll look at me and smile♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.07,0:46:52.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ I'll understand♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.61,0:46:56.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And in a little while♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.11,0:46:59.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ He'll take my hand♪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.68,0:47:03.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And though it seems absurd♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.32,0:47:11.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪I know we both won't say a word♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.06,0:47:19.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪Maybe I shall meet him Sunday♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.07,0:47:22.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ Maybe Monday♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.94,0:47:27.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ Maybe not♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.71,0:47:31.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪Still I'm sure to meet him...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.85,0:47:35.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Imagine if we had this when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.45,0:47:37.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No fear, no shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.95,0:47:46.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All I was imagining all those years was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.99,0:47:50.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ He'll build a little home♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.96,0:47:54.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ Just meant for two♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.70,0:47:58.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪From which I'll never roam♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.27,0:48:01.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ Who would, would you?♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.81,0:48:06.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And so all else above♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.15,0:48:09.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ I'm waiting for the man...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.75,0:48:13.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Felix Turner, would you like to move in with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.05,0:48:14.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.65,0:48:16.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yes? - Yes-terday
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.09,0:48:18.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.09,0:48:23.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪And so all else above...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.40,0:48:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪I'm waiting for the man♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.00,0:48:38.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ I love.♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.62,0:48:48.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are all walking time bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.99,0:48:51.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,waiting for whatever it is to set us off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.20,0:48:58.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,C'mon, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:49:01.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If this article doesn't scare the shit out of you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.47,0:49:04.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Gay men may have no future here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.13,0:49:07.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Our continued existence depends on just how angry you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:13.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They turned us away from foreign emergency rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.16,0:49:14.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.03,0:49:15.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think he's lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.81,0:49:16.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,D, where can I take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.71,0:49:18.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Put him on the couch there. I'll call Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.24,0:49:21.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- God damn it! - I'll get some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.78,0:49:23.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How long has he been like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.39,0:49:25.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,A couple hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.66,0:49:30.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you asked me that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.93,0:49:33.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What do I think? I know that the government
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.63,0:49:37.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is intentionally ignoring this epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.23,0:49:40.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're accusing the government of the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.34,0:49:43.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,of a conspiracy to murder all gay men?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.98,0:49:51.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, you can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.35,0:49:53.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, Sarabeth, I am. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.38,0:49:56.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That is a powerful accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.08,0:49:58.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is an epidemic
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.19,0:50:00.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and it's being ignored by the United States government.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.29,0:50:02.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Intentionally? - Intentionally being ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:04.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is a national emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.29,0:50:06.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is an epidemic. It's a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.13,0:50:09.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't go on national TV accuse the government of murder, Ned
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.16,0:50:11.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Why not? - Because one day we're gonna get money
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.97,0:50:13.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,research grants.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.39,0:50:15.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Congress still hasn't appropriated a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.30,0:50:16.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The mayor's still on and on!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:20.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned when you go public you have no right to speak for this organization
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.21,0:50:24.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,unless we have approved what you have to say in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.38,0:50:26.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In point of fact, you aren't even an officer of this organization
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.98,0:50:29.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and you shouldn't be speaking for us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.18,0:50:32.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for sharing that with me, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.83,0:50:47.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you think the city has been so slow
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.57,0:50:50.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to acknowledge and deal with this emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.50,0:50:52.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you're implying that the city has recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:50:55.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and acknowledged this emergency, Malcolm. It has not.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.14,0:50:57.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why not, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.04,0:50:58.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Because the mayor's gay
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.58,0:51:00.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and he's scared shitless out of his panties it'll blow his cover
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.98,0:51:02.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.55,0:51:04.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Take it off, get it off. - Are we still rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.88,0:51:07.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't tell me what to say when I'm speaking for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.52,0:51:09.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Bullshit. They all know you're one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:10.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It is totally and politically incorrect
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:13.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to call someone gay who does not self-identify as being gay
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.43,0:51:15.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know it's been that way forever
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.06,0:51:17.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,but something different is going on here now. We're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.43,0:51:19.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The mayor, he's a personal friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.23,0:51:21.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You want him to appoint you a judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.07,0:51:23.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you have a little conflict of interest going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.27,0:51:24.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I told you I sent him a memo. - When?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.90,0:51:26.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Through channels. - When?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:28.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- He'll answer me. - When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.27,0:51:30.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,There's 110 new cases this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.61,0:51:33.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Still no meeting with our gay mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.18,0:51:35.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No meeting with his gay assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.85,0:51:41.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What? Do I embarrass you, Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.12,0:51:43.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.45,0:51:44.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You get more with honey than with vinegar, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.72,0:51:46.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,God, no one's told me that one, Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.12,0:51:48.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, obviously, they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.23,0:51:49.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I never believed that bullshit, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.96,0:51:51.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are in over our heads with the patients we're trying to help
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.96,0:51:55.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tommy, will you please read this report out loud for Ned?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.10,0:51:59.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have trained 25 crisis counselors
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.07,0:52:01.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to help the newly diagnosed in whatever needs that they might have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.91,0:52:05.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have 12 group leaders who meet with these counselors
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.54,0:52:07.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,at least once a week to go over their clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.64,0:52:09.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,There are now 17 volunteer social workers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.45,0:52:12.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,psychologists and/or psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.02,0:52:13.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We helped draw up 75 wills last...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.65,0:52:16.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,75, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.42,0:52:18.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You used to be a fighter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.12,0:52:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Did you like being in the Green Berets? - Yes. I loved it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.06,0:52:23.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you completely forgotten how to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.09,0:52:25.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't tell me how to fight. I just fight differently than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.70,0:52:27.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I haven't seen your way yet. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.66,0:52:30.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Bruce... Albert may be dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.40,0:52:33.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch! You say another word about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.30,0:52:36.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.04,0:52:37.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.94,0:52:40.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You have no right being on this board
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.51,0:52:42.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,unless you put pressure on your friend the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:45.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you to join us in the first place and you know it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.59,0:52:59.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- No, no, I'm not gonna do that. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.70,0:53:01.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you got your free legal work from my firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.43,0:53:03.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna be on your board of directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.20,0:53:05.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's only for the stationery. You don't have to do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.57,0:53:08.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That is just an evasion. If you thought this was a straight disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.64,0:53:09.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you being gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.92,0:53:11.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What else does it have to do with?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.01,0:53:13.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,One of these days, I'm gonna get you to agree
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.38,0:53:15.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that over 20 million men and women in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.58,0:53:18.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,don't require the services of a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.38,0:53:19.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.68,0:53:21.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, I read stuff, I see TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.88,0:53:23.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Guys in leather and chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.89,0:53:25.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dresses, high heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.65,0:53:27.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I say to myself, "This isn't Ned."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.49,0:53:30.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know the media always dramatizes the most extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.29,0:53:32.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You guys have a dreadful image problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.49,0:53:35.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why it's so important to have people like you supporting us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.43,0:53:37.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You already have your dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.13,0:53:39.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We better get to lunch. I've got an important meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.73,0:53:41.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you? How important?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.94,0:53:43.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm asking for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.57,0:53:46.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In every area I consider important, you have my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.67,0:53:49.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The only area that I consider important
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.14,0:53:52.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't have your support at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.08,0:53:54.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In some place deep down inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.15,0:53:55.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,you still think I'm sick, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.42,0:53:57.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you've adjusted to life pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.18,0:54:00.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- All things considered. - I saw how unhappy you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.59,0:54:02.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So were you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.19,0:54:05.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You wound up going to shrinks, too. We grew up side by side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.93,0:54:08.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We both felt the same about Mom and Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.70,0:54:13.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I agree to the fact that I have any number of awful character traits
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.07,0:54:16.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,but not to the fact that whatever awful things they did to us
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.90,0:54:20.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,made me sick and gay while you stayed straight and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.74,0:54:22.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't all react the same way to the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.84,0:54:25.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So you became a lawyer and I became a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.21,0:54:27.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, we have a difference of opinion over theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.41,0:54:30.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But your theory turns me into a man from Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.12,0:54:32.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My theory doesn't do that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.58,0:54:34.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting I did something wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.92,0:54:37.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,in sending you into therapy so young?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.22,0:54:38.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were gonna stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.76,0:54:40.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't think that I'd had done anything wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.46,0:54:42.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,until you sent me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.43,0:54:46.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ben... you mean more to me than anyone in the whole world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.27,0:54:49.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You always have. Ben, you gotta say it. - Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.77,0:54:52.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you. Just say it. Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.08,0:55:03.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.61,0:55:06.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.75,0:55:08.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.86,0:55:13.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Every time I lose this fight, it hurts more.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.89,0:55:16.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm going home. - Oh, come on, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.29,0:55:17.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.93,0:55:19.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Sarah still loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.43,0:55:21.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- The cat still loves you. - This is not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.60,0:55:25.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You have my love, my legal advice, my financial supervision
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.84,0:55:28.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't give you the courage to stand up to me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.07,0:55:30.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and say you don't give a flying fuck about what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.91,0:55:32.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Everybody's oppressed by somebody else
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.68,0:55:35.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,in some form or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.38,0:55:38.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Most of us learn to fight against it despite people's opinions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.58,0:55:40.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,without the help of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.55,0:55:44.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And stop trying to wring some kind of admission of guilt out of me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.32,0:55:47.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Agreeing that you were born just the same as I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:48.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,isn't gonna save your dying friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.69,0:55:52.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That is exactly what is going to save my dying friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.33,0:55:55.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You make it sound like I'm the enemy. - I am beginning to think
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.27,0:55:57.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that you and your straight world are our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.67,0:55:59.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am furious with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.94,0:56:04.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And every goddamn doctor who made me feel it was sick to love a man
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.27,0:56:06.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am trying to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.38,0:56:09.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,why nobody gives a shit that we're dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.51,0:56:15.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,$5 million for a house? We can't even get 27 cents from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.85,0:56:20.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know 43 guys who have died and you say it's my cause not yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.39,0:56:23.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You still think I'm sick
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.13,0:56:27.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I simply cannot allow it for one single second longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.30,0:56:32.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not speak to you again until you accept me as your equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.57,0:56:34.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your healthy equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.37,0:56:36.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.98,0:56:45.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, be careful with that, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:48.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- That is a precious antique. - Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.35,0:56:50.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm thinking we should put that in the grand salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.35,0:56:52.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do we have a basement? That's where it should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.19,0:56:54.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Bella, I think it's time we moved your filthy mouth above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.82,0:56:56.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll decorate tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.92,0:56:58.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Just shove it all in there the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.69,0:57:00.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.40,0:57:03.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, knock it off, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.10,0:57:05.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.17,0:57:08.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yes, hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.50,0:57:10.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My name is Estelle
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.74,0:57:14.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and my best friend Harvey died last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.01,0:57:20.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We went everywhere together, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.71,0:57:23.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Like Broadway and the Rockettes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.58,0:57:25.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and ice skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.12,0:57:30.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He was a beautiful skater.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.12,0:57:31.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.96,0:57:35.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But he didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.63,0:57:38.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.70,0:57:41.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn it, I wanna do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.37,0:57:42.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though all my lesbian friends say
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.97,0:57:44.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"What have you guys ever done for us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.77,0:57:49.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.44,0:57:51.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is for Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.58,0:57:55.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Please... tell me you can use me for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.76,0:58:07.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I need a hotline director. You think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.06,0:58:09.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I don't know how. - I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.03,0:58:13.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.23,0:58:17.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me buy you a cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.44,0:58:20.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- and we'll figure this out, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.28,0:58:34.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- So, you want to set up here? - Yeah, this is good. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.35,0:58:37.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- What are you doing? - We're from the NBC affiliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.26,0:58:39.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- So? - This is the new Gay Men's Health Crisis office?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.92,0:58:42.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Who are you? - I'm Bruce Niles. I'm the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.66,0:58:45.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't sign any consent form for you to film me or this establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.43,0:58:48.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Please turn it off and leave. - Hey, now, don't touch my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.53,0:58:51.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Who sent you here? - Somebody named Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.84,0:58:53.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Weeks. - Oh, great. You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.91,0:58:55.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Anybody homo?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.41,0:58:56.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.71,0:58:58.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello, is this thing rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.38,0:59:01.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at this. We're in both of them the same week.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.55,0:59:03.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Every major network
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.41,0:59:06.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and now finally our very first office.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.02,0:59:09.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanna introduce you to our gay president who's in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.19,0:59:11.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And he's so handsome. Don't ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.52,0:59:15.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a very handsome cover boy going to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.43,0:59:20.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, great. Now you fight. Great. Fight, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.28,0:59:22.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You made me sound like a coward and I'm not a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.47,0:59:24.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what? You have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.13,0:59:26.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your brother invests for you so you have income.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.24,0:59:29.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can be gay 24/7, Ned, but I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.11,0:59:30.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't! So fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.77,0:59:31.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, fuck you, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.94,0:59:35.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.91,0:59:40.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,When I look at you, I am filled with despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.58,0:59:43.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,When I look at you, I worry we're not gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.09,0:59:45.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you think this country was founded?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.09,0:59:47.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought I was getting started with Paul Revere
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.26,0:59:49.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,not some coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.96,0:59:54.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned, look at me. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.43,0:59:56.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.23,0:59:59.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are doomed if we do it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.37,1:00:00.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Doomed! - How are they going to help us
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.97,1:00:02.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,if they don't know who we are?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.24,1:00:04.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They won't help us, Ned, if they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.71,1:00:14.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! Hey! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.62,1:00:19.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Holy shit. - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.97,1:00:37.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get it, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.24,1:00:39.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello? Yeah, you are our very first call.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.61,1:00:42.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.74,1:00:46.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you have the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.22,1:00:53.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You each gotta pull your shit together now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.45,1:00:58.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you need to stop being such a fucking drama queen. God damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.59,1:01:02.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is Estelle.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:06.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.57,1:01:09.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.95,1:01:34.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:01.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, we have four hands and two incomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.75,1:02:03.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not getting any younger, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.19,1:02:06.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, let's leave my age out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.97,1:02:17.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Very beautiful, the country. - Very quiet, the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.37,1:02:21.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no. Don't you dare
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.61,1:02:23.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.94,1:02:27.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You didn't leave this number on your machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.48,1:02:30.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You promised. - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.35,1:02:32.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I do think we should picket the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.38,1:02:37.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I said that and I stand by that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.45,1:02:39.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.92,1:02:43.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.70,1:02:51.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And every gay man who is unable to come forward
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.83,1:02:53.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and fight to save his own life
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.30,1:02:55.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is truly helping to kill the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.77,1:02:58.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How many of us have to die before you get scared off your ass
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.37,1:03:00.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and into action? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.95,1:03:05.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:08.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I hear it's being called the "Ned Weeks School of Outrage."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.39,1:03:13.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I did speak to one of our science reporters.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.69,1:03:15.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.06,1:03:18.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It turns out he's gay and he won't...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.26,1:03:20.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,don't yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.63,1:03:25.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All those shrinks, they must have done something right
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.93,1:03:28.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Ritvo,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.54,1:03:30.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Dr. Malev, - Malev.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.71,1:03:33.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillespie,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.34,1:03:34.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Patty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.88,1:03:37.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Maxene, Dr. LaVerne.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.31,1:03:41.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why does that have to take so long?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.05,1:03:43.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All you ever eat is desserts.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.35,1:03:44.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Sugar's the most important thing in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.92,1:03:47.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All the rest is just to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.73,1:03:58.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.27,1:04:00.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- What? - The fucking board.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.03,1:04:03.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They say I'm causing a panic, that I'm making myself a celebrity
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.10,1:04:05.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Not one of them will be interviewed or appear on TV
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.31,1:04:07.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,so I do it all by default.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.74,1:04:10.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're becoming a leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.08,1:04:12.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- And you love to fight. - I like to fight? Moi?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.48,1:04:14.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who, you? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.65,1:04:16.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're havin' a great time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.82,1:04:18.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.35,1:04:22.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's funny, I never wanted to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.82,1:04:25.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.79,1:04:27.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's sad how much time we lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.13,1:04:29.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We just weren't ready then.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.57,1:04:39.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If I had it...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.24,1:04:41.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,would you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.72,1:04:45.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.96,1:04:50.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you if I did?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.29,1:04:51.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.73,1:04:54.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.33,1:04:57.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Because my mother ran the local chapter of the Red Cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.17,1:05:00.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,She put me to work in the Bloodmobile when I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.44,1:05:04.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not programmed for anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.24,1:05:09.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned, I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.78,1:05:12.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're finally pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.55,1:05:17.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was married once.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.72,1:05:22.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You never told me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.79,1:05:25.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.09,1:05:26.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,she said I had been unfair to her
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.89,1:05:29.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,which I had been.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.00,1:05:34.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I have a son. - You have a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.97,1:05:38.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- She won't let me see him. - You can't see your own son?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.64,1:05:41.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But didn't you fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.24,1:05:42.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That means you're ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.91,1:05:45.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So he will be, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.18,1:05:47.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is why I didn't tell you. Who says I didn't fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.48,1:05:49.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.38,1:05:52.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What happens to people who can't be as strong as you want them to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.35,1:05:54.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Weakness scares the shit out of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.69,1:05:57.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My father was weak, and I'm afraid I'll be like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.86,1:06:00.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,His life didn't stand for anything and then it was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.83,1:06:02.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So I fight, constantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.86,1:06:04.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And if I can do it, I can't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.56,1:06:07.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,why everybody else can't do it, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.33,1:06:08.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.67,1:06:10.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Felix! Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.54,1:06:18.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Felix. I didn't mean anything by that, Felix.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.01,1:06:20.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I... I... I'm scared of... lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.65,1:06:24.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Really. Heights. I never told you I'm terrified of...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.42,1:06:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.60,1:06:44.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It keeps getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.54,1:06:46.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It doesn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.95,1:07:00.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Felix?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.62,1:07:06.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who, may I ask, is Felix?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.99,1:07:10.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never been so in love in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.63,1:07:14.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Never been in love in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.30,1:07:17.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell him to come to see me first thing tomorrow 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.94,1:07:20.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned, God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.35,1:07:22.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do? Not be with anybody ever?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.94,1:07:26.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not as easy as you might think.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.01,1:07:27.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Em, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.98,1:07:29.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.85,1:07:33.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.65,1:07:36.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was five years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.62,1:07:38.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,A woman from the Bahamas came to our town
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.42,1:07:39.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,carrying the polio virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.59,1:07:43.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,She... stayed with friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.03,1:07:45.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Their kid was in my kindergarten class.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.53,1:07:48.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Four of us in that class got polio.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.53,1:07:53.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was all dressed up in my Halloween costume
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.44,1:07:55.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to go trick-or-treating
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.27,1:07:58.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and my mother felt my forehead, put me to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.41,1:08:02.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night, I realized my whole body
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.55,1:08:05.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,except my arms and my hands were paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.28,1:08:07.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was crying out for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.32,1:08:10.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"I can't move, I can't move."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.02,1:08:13.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They rushed me to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.72,1:08:15.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,were told I'd be dead in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.79,1:08:17.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I fought. I lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.43,1:08:19.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you in an iron lung?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.76,1:08:21.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.83,1:08:24.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I was in bed at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.00,1:08:29.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was connected to my class with this little...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.71,1:08:32.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Little loudspeaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.74,1:08:36.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All the children were required to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.41,1:08:40.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We would say, "Hello,"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.82,1:08:43.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and then not know what to say next.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.08,1:08:45.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They were all terrified of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.22,1:08:46.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Still are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:48.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I scare the shit out of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.86,1:08:51.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The "holy terror" in a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.33,1:08:54.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm scaring people, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.60,1:08:57.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Learn how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.40,1:09:00.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't need everybody's love and approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.54,1:09:04.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned, your organization is... worthless.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.47,1:09:06.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't get anyone important on the board.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.91,1:09:09.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've seen over 300 patients. Me. One doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.34,1:09:12.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All these guys who made millions off of us...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.05,1:09:15.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,fashion, rock, movies, real estate, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.72,1:09:18.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And any time Bruce doesn't agree with me
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.32,1:09:20.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- he puts it to a board vote. - And you lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.59,1:09:22.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't pass along sex recommendations
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.96,1:09:25.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,or any information that isn't 100% certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.03,1:09:28.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing is 100% certain in science.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.13,1:09:29.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It wouldn't matter what you say anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.60,1:09:31.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't yell at me for what I'm not doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.43,1:09:33.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- What the fuck is your side doing? - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.53,1:09:35.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where's your A.M.A.?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.40,1:09:39.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Does being Jewish always make you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.94,1:09:42.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'm not Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.54,1:09:45.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm German.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.88,1:09:49.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Everybody thinks you're Jewish. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.45,1:09:51.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In medicine it helps.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.65,1:09:57.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You stayed in bed the whole way through school?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.99,1:10:00.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,By college I had my first braces
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.56,1:10:03.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I could walk... a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.70,1:10:05.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't walk so good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.10,1:10:07.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Probably because I'm too busy to practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.40,1:10:09.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You must practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.80,1:10:12.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.44,1:10:14.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.61,1:10:17.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't scratch my Mathis.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.28,1:10:28.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,May I have this dance
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.82,1:10:34.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. You asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.20,1:10:40.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,My crutches.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.96,1:10:46.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ The moment you come into view ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.04,1:10:49.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ Chances are you think♪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.54,1:10:59.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.12,1:11:05.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mm-mm. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.96,1:11:11.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Oh... - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.89,1:11:14.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.15,1:11:38.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to leave him alone now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.82,1:11:41.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm afraid a cure won't come in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.92,1:11:46.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of my anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.29,1:11:50.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm a terrible leader and... - A lousy dancer. Put me back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.12,1:12:11.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Polio is a virus, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.12,1:12:20.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Nobody gets polio anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.65,1:12:49.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Where is he? We've been here for an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.06,1:12:52.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are these people? We're in a fucking dungeon here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.99,1:12:56.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He can't do this to us. He cannot do this to us and get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.73,1:13:00.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Did you start? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.43,1:13:01.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Okay, God, hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.94,1:13:03.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, what a tomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.70,1:13:05.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Do they not want us to be seen above ground?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.87,1:13:07.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And where is he? I'm an hour late.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.67,1:13:10.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ned: Hour and a half. - Don't start on me, lamb chop.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.14,1:13:13.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Tommy, where were you? - I was up at Bellevue.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.31,1:13:17.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Had to put a sweet dying child together with his mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.12,1:13:20.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They hadn't seen each other for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.79,1:13:22.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He never told her he was gay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.72,1:13:26.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He didn't want to see her. He refused to see her for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.19,1:13:29.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, he was angry when I waltzed in with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.83,1:13:34.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It was a real weeper. Mama holding her son.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.53,1:13:37.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.94,1:13:41.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry I'm late. I'm Hiram Keebler.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.87,1:13:44.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello. Are you related to the folks who make the crackers?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.74,1:13:47.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm kidding. I'm Tommy Boatwright.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.28,1:13:49.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned Weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.71,1:13:51.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Bruce Niles. I'm the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.95,1:13:53.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The mayor wants you to know how much he cares
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.82,1:13:58.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,how impressed he’s with how you've been shouldering your own responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.66,1:14:00.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Thank you. - Thank you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.26,1:14:02.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Responsibilities? Everything we're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.16,1:14:04.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is the stuff you guys should be doing and we need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.26,1:14:05.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, what Mr. Weeks is trying to say, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.86,1:14:07.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is that... we're swamped.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.56,1:14:11.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're fielding over 500 calls a day on our emergency hotline.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.50,1:14:13.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And we're providing information that, quite frankly
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.70,1:14:15.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,the city should be providing, and isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.84,1:14:17.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Sir, we need office space. We have one small room.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.97,1:14:20.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have over 100 people calling or walking in and out every day
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.54,1:14:22.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and plus it's real hard when people don't want to rent to us
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.71,1:14:24.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,because we're... - Whoa. That's illegal discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.68,1:14:26.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know that to be true, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.18,1:14:28.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Keebler, it is not illegal to discriminate against homosexuals.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.89,1:14:31.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for 14 months to see the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.32,1:14:33.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's taken us a year to get this meeting with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.49,1:14:34.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're an hour and a half late.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.60,1:14:36.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you told the mayor there's an epidemic going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.95,1:14:38.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Uh, says who? - The government.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.20,1:14:39.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Which government? What? Our government?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.96,1:14:42.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- An epidemic? - The Centers for Disease Control declared it...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.30,1:14:44.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- 17 months ago. - You can't not know this!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.33,1:14:46.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Could you please reduce your level of hysteria?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.30,1:14:47.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.84,1:14:52.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,New York City, San Francisco, Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.14,1:14:56.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Chicago, Boston, Denver. Every single major American city
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.08,1:14:57.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is now showing cases.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.61,1:15:00.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,At least 25 foreign countries. But New York City
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.42,1:15:02.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,our home, the city that you have pledged to protect
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.92,1:15:04.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,has more than half of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.42,1:15:06.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Half the cases, half the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.22,1:15:08.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know 57 of the dead ones. I don't wanna know any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.99,1:15:10.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, when do we get to see the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.96,1:15:13.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,14 months is a long time to be out to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.06,1:15:16.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You wait a minute. - No, you wait a minute. We can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.20,1:15:18.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Time is not on our side.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.10,1:15:20.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, if you won't take word to the mayor, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.20,1:15:22.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hire a hunky hustler and send him up to Gracie Mansion
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.77,1:15:24.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,with a plea tattooed to his cock?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.64,1:15:28.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mayor Koch is not gay! - Oh, come on, "Blanche."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.48,1:15:33.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.11,1:15:35.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you think I want to help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.92,1:15:38.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I have a friend who is dying of this shit
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.49,1:15:40.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,right now in the V.A. hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.92,1:15:44.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's very tricky. You can see that. It is very tricky.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.76,1:15:47.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tricky, shit! There are a million gay people in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.13,1:15:48.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,A million and one counting you!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.93,1:15:51.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what? A fire goes out in a school furnace
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.50,1:15:55.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,on the West Side. I get 3,000 calls in one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.74,1:15:57.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.61,1:16:00.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,If so many of you are so upset, why do I only hear from this loudmouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.91,1:16:04.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- That's a very good question. - Okay, so there are half a million
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.48,1:16:08.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,gay men in our area. 315 cases doesn't seem too high
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.32,1:16:10.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,considering how many of us... of you there are.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.72,1:16:13.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- This is bullshit! - Ned, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.09,1:16:14.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, I understand this is tricky, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.99,1:16:17.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- But we need your help - I think, that is, that the mayor thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.46,1:16:19.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,you guys are overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.16,1:16:23.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You tell that cocksucker he is a selfish, heartless son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.37,1:16:32.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You are Michael R. Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.34,1:16:34.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You hold an unsecure job with the city's Department of Health.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.67,1:16:37.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd watch out for your friends if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.09,1:16:50.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't believe that just happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.39,1:16:53.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mickey, I am going on "The Today Show" tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.03,1:16:54.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I am telling them
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.59,1:16:57.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that the mayor just threatened your job to shut us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.30,1:16:59.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"The Today Show"? You're gonna what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.43,1:17:02.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They are treating us like shit and we're allowing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.47,1:17:05.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, politicians, the only thing they really respond to is pressure
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.97,1:17:08.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You heard him with his "3,000 West Side calls."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.97,1:17:10.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're not yelling loud enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.85,1:17:18.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Get your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.32,1:17:20.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Get your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.74,1:17:40.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- This is Tommy. - Tommy, it's Ned.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.77,1:17:44.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hey. - Nick died.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.51,1:17:46.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.78,1:17:48.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,God damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.78,1:17:52.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll call later when I know more about the memorial.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.02,1:18:02.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I have this tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.73,1:18:06.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's something I do now when a friend dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.97,1:18:12.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I save his Rolodex card.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.37,1:18:14.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.07,1:18:16.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Throw it away in the trash can?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.17,1:18:18.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.01,1:18:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.88,1:18:21.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's too final.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.28,1:18:28.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Last year I had five cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.72,1:18:31.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Now I have 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.62,1:18:34.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,A collection of cardboard tombstones
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.36,1:18:36.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,bound together with a rubber band.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.36,1:18:40.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate these fuckin' funerals.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:43.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.20,1:18:45.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you know what else I hate?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.87,1:18:47.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate the memorials.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.97,1:18:50.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's our social life now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.34,1:18:52.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Going to these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.51,1:19:01.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Nick was a choreographer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.65,1:19:04.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know if any of you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.72,1:19:08.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He was just starting out. He didn't tell a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.02,1:19:11.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He was waiting to invite you to his
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.09,1:19:13.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,big debut at Carnegie Hall or some shit
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.43,1:19:15.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,so we could all be proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.97,1:19:22.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But he was so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.30,1:19:24.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He had such promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.08,1:19:30.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're losing an entire generation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.45,1:19:34.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Young men at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.62,1:19:37.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Just gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.05,1:19:40.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Choreographers, playwrights
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.89,1:19:43.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,dancers, actors.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.29,1:19:48.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All those plays that won't get written now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.96,1:19:54.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All those dances never to be danced.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.07,1:20:02.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,In closing, I'm just gonna say I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.64,1:20:04.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm fuckin' mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.18,1:20:09.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I keep screaming inside, "Why are they letting us die?"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.42,1:20:13.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"Why is no one helping us?"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.92,1:20:19.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And here's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.46,1:20:21.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Here's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.63,1:20:26.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They just don't like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.07,1:21:44.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to beat this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.44,1:21:46.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've always been lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.61,1:21:52.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Good. That's the right attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.95,1:21:57.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted a job on the "Times," I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.52,1:21:59.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted Ned.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.56,1:22:07.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Have I given it to Ned?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.20,1:22:09.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.00,1:22:17.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,One person has a cold
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.34,1:22:19.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,sometimes the partner catches it, sometimes not.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.28,1:22:24.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Some doctors are saying it's okay if we use condoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.05,1:22:26.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I know they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.16,1:22:42.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Can we kiss? - Felix.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.23,1:22:43.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You have nothing to fight back with.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.93,1:22:45.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You have no immune system to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.63,1:22:48.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your body is now open to every conceivable type of infection.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.67,1:22:50.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.17,1:22:54.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to do my damnedest, so must you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.24,1:22:56.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I bet you say that to all the boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.08,1:22:58.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.51,1:23:00.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.10,1:23:26.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:38.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Once upon a time there was a little boy
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.82,1:23:42.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,who always wanted to love another little boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.36,1:23:44.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,One day he finally found that love
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.49,1:23:46.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and it was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.06,1:23:49.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to use gloves.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.56,1:23:52.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to do this. I'm supposed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.00,1:23:54.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to not kiss him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.13,1:23:57.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm so sorry. - I'm not supposed to be only 45 years old
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.37,1:24:00.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and taking care of a 35-year-old young man
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.34,1:24:02.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,who's 100 years old and dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.05,1:24:09.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Emma calls it a seesaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.22,1:24:12.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's fine, he gets sick
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.79,1:24:15.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,he gets better...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.46,1:24:19.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,he gets sicker.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.36,1:24:22.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,God help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.47,1:24:37.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's afraid I'll leave him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.98,1:24:41.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I told him I wouldn't leave him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.78,1:24:45.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That I never for one second would think of leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.12,1:24:47.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But he doesn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.39,1:24:53.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe in much these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.06,1:24:56.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But we must never stop believing in each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.80,1:25:05.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a mess. That's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.27,1:25:12.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You cry and you cry until you think can't cry anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.34,1:25:16.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and then you cry some more.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.62,1:25:26.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Not only for yourself or Felix, but for all the little boys
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.39,1:25:28.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,who finally found their other little boys
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.26,1:25:31.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,they've wanted all their lives now that we're men.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.67,1:25:38.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,G.M.H.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.94,1:25:40.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Estelle speaking. How may I assist you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.70,1:25:42.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Someone needs a will!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.54,1:25:44.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where's Ned? I want to speak to him. - He's in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.51,1:25:45.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Here, give him this number. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.91,1:25:47.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- G.M.H.C. - G.M.H.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.24,1:25:51.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tommy, I think I got us maybe four qualified social workers to volunteer
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.15,1:25:54.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- They're all lesbians. - Thank God for the lesbians.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.28,1:25:56.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Your anus?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.52,1:25:59.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Planet Uranus.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.39,1:26:02.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.06,1:26:04.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mickey, why aren't you in Rio?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.29,1:26:07.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I put the phones on service. You guys should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.03,1:26:09.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't want any burnouts.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.50,1:26:11.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Good night, Phil. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.83,1:26:13.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Night, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.17,1:26:14.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Bye, baby. - Good night, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.34,1:26:16.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.57,1:26:18.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.48,1:26:24.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Phil got diagnosed today.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.08,1:26:31.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mickey, why aren't you on vacation in Rio?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.65,1:26:33.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I was in Rio. Gregory...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.79,1:26:35.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I were in Rio.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.96,1:26:37.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I get a call from Hiram's office
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.99,1:26:41.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,saying I should be in his office right away first thing this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.19,1:26:44.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,From Rio? What kind of meeting?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.16,1:26:48.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I get to City Hall, Hiram keeps me waiting forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.17,1:26:51.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And finally the commissioner comes out and he says
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.07,1:26:55.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that Hiram doesn't want to see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.44,1:27:01.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted to scream, "I haven't slept in two days, you dumb fuck."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.25,1:27:04.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,But I didn't. Instead I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.22,1:27:06.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,"Please, sir, then...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.25,1:27:10.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,why did he make me come all the way back from Rio?"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.32,1:27:13.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And he says, "Oh, I'm afraid he didn't take me into his confidence."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.99,1:27:16.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And he walks off.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.93,1:27:21.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned's article attacking Hiram just came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.53,1:27:25.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose my job because Ned doesn't like himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.17,1:27:27.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that, Mick?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.94,1:27:30.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You keep trying to get us to say things that we don't wanna say
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.94,1:27:32.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I don't think we can afford
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.55,1:27:34.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to make so many enemies before we have enough friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.95,1:27:37.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry Spaulding is calling all of his friends
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.75,1:27:40.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,from under his oxygen tank to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.32,1:27:42.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tibby Maurer took an overdose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.65,1:27:45.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hal Schechter has got stumps for feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.72,1:27:50.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Frannie Santuzza's lost his mind! - Will you stop it? Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.63,1:27:53.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mickey, you all right? - I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.27,1:27:57.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why can't they find the virus?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.67,1:27:59.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Baby, it takes time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.54,1:28:02.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I work all day for the city writing stuff on...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.84,1:28:04.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,breast-feeding versus formula
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.68,1:28:06.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and how to stay calm when you have herpes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.51,1:28:09.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And at night I work on our newsletter and our health column for the "Native."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.65,1:28:13.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just... I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.05,1:28:16.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I have written about every single theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.92,1:28:18.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Repeated infection by a virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.92,1:28:20.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,New appearance by a dormant virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.69,1:28:25.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Single virus, new virus, old virus, multi-virus, partial virus,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.23,1:28:27.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- latent virus, mutant virus... - Tommy: Take it easy, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.73,1:28:30.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No, we mustn't forget about fucking and sucking
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.40,1:28:31.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and kissing and blood and voodoo
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.97,1:28:33.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and drugs and poppers and needles
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.74,1:28:36.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and Africa, Haiti, Cuba, blacks
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.01,1:28:40.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,amoebas, pigs, fucking Uranus!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.98,1:28:47.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- What if it isn't any of them? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.42,1:28:50.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The great plague of London was caused by drinking water from a pump
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.52,1:28:53.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that just nobody... nobody noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.56,1:28:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe it's predisposition or the theory of the herd...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.43,1:29:02.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,only so many of us are going to get it, then the pool's used up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.90,1:29:05.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What if it's monogamy? Bruce, you and I
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.33,1:29:07.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,could actually be worse off
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.67,1:29:10.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,because of constant bombardment from a single source...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.31,1:29:12.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,our lovers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.21,1:29:13.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So maybe the guys who go to the baths
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.81,1:29:15.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,maybe they've built up the best immunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.51,1:29:18.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know what to tell anybody anymore and everybody asks me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.91,1:29:20.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who's right? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.48,1:29:22.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Who's wrong? I feel...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.42,1:29:25.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I feel so fucking inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.12,1:29:28.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,How can we tell people, "Stop"?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.26,1:29:32.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just... I don't... it might be caused by...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.13,1:29:33.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.70,1:29:36.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,That's exactly how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.53,1:29:38.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And maybe he's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.87,1:29:40.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And that scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.47,1:29:42.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Neddy, you scare me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.84,1:29:45.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You really think the president...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.24,1:29:48.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that he wants this to happen? You really think the CIA
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.18,1:29:50.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,has unleashed germ warfare
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.11,1:29:53.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,to kill off all the queers that Jerry Falwell doesn't want?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.11,1:29:56.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mick. Try to hold on. - To what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.48,1:29:58.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I used to love my country.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.39,1:30:00.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The "Native" received an anonymous letter describing
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.39,1:30:03.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,top-secret Defense Department experiments at Fort Detrick, Maryland...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.79,1:30:07.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,that have produced a virus that can destroy the immune system.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.49,1:30:09.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Its codename was "Firm Hand."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.63,1:30:12.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They started testing it in 1978 on a group of gays.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.63,1:30:13.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I never used to believe shit like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.97,1:30:15.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,they're gonna persecute us!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.94,1:30:17.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,They're gonna cancel our health insurance
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.77,1:30:19.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,they're gonna put us into camps, they're gonna quarantine us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.47,1:30:21.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you think that I'm killing people?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.34,1:30:24.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- That is not what I said. - It is, you know you said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.71,1:30:28.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've spent 15 years of my life
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.75,1:30:30.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,fighting for our right to be free
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.55,1:30:32.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and to make love wherever, whenever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.52,1:30:34.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're telling me all those years
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.05,1:30:37.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,of what being gay stood for is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.06,1:30:40.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And that I'm a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.76,1:30:45.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have been so oppressed. Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.10,1:30:49.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Can't you see how important it is for us to love openly
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.24,1:30:52.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,without hiding, without guilt?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.34,1:30:54.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Why can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.45,1:31:01.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I went to the top of the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.64,1:31:03.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm taking you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.03,1:31:04.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You can jump off from there when nobody's looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.75,1:31:07.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, Mickey, let's go home. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.83,1:31:15.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned, I'm not a murderer. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.10,1:31:19.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,All my life I've been hated for being gay
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.86,1:31:21.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,for being short
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.63,1:31:23.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.30,1:31:24.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So go ahead, you tell everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.87,1:31:27.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell everybody that we were wrong and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.04,1:31:29.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Someday, somebody's gonna come along
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.57,1:31:31.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and they're gonna stick the knife in you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.38,1:31:34.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and tell you everything you fought for your whole life is shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.61,1:31:35.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.78,1:31:38.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mickey! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.52,1:31:40.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Get up. Come here. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.19,1:31:42.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.35,1:31:45.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take you home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.49,1:31:49.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go home. Take me to St. Vincent's.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.56,1:31:52.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. That's fine. Come. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.67,1:31:57.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, we're all real tired, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.84,1:32:02.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We got ourselves here a lot of bereavement overload.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.88,1:32:11.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're the fighters. Aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.78,1:32:14.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're the fi... - You bet, sweetness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.42,1:32:17.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're a hero. YOU HEAR ME?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.22,1:32:21.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a hero whether you know that or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.16,1:32:23.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're our first hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.16,1:32:25.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.54,1:32:36.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You wanna be president?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.54,1:32:38.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I just want Felix to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.82,1:32:53.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Gay Men's Health Crisis.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.29,1:32:56.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiram, old buddy. How's it hanging?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.60,1:33:06.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.57,1:33:13.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- You ready? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.14,1:33:15.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The mayor's found a secret little fund
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.11,1:33:17.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,for giving away money secretly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.48,1:33:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are not allowed to tell anyone where we got it,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.88,1:33:22.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and if we do, we'll never get any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.98,1:33:25.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- How much? - $9,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.49,1:33:28.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Ned.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.09,1:33:34.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Albert's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.06,1:33:40.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,His mother wanted to see him in Phoenix before he died.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.47,1:33:44.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And this was the last week, when it was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.74,1:33:49.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So I got permission from Emma and took him to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.88,1:33:59.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And when we got to the airport
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.79,1:34:02.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,the pilot refused to fly the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.92,1:34:05.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So I refused to get off of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.09,1:34:10.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You would have been very proud of me, Ned.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.90,1:34:13.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,So finally we get another pilot
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.50,1:34:18.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and when we take off
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.50,1:34:21.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Albert just loses his mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.84,1:34:23.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be in this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.21,1:34:25.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's okay. - I don't wanna be in this...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.58,1:34:28.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm just gonna go. - No, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.48,1:34:30.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.35,1:34:32.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Albert. - Tell him to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.85,1:34:37.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. - Sir, sir, you have to keep seated.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.79,1:34:41.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Sit down up there. - Sir, have a seat. You have to...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.23,1:34:43.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.53,1:34:44.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Sir... - Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.70,1:34:46.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.40,1:34:49.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We gotta sit down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.90,1:34:53.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He doesn't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.37,1:34:54.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,It's me. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.87,1:34:56.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't know where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.98,1:34:59.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- We're almost home. - That we're going to see his mother
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.14,1:35:03.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,in Phoenix... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.11,1:35:05.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He just becomes...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.98,1:35:09.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, shit. Can I get a goddamn towel, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.15,1:35:13.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,When we land in Phoenix and when we get to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.36,1:35:16.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,where his mother had fixed up the room real nice...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.46,1:35:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Albert is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.14,1:35:29.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The hospital doctors refused to examine him
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.91,1:35:32.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and give him a cause of death on his death certificate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.51,1:35:36.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Without the death certificate, the undertakers will not take him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.21,1:35:39.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- And neither would the police. - Come on, man. Pull it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.95,1:35:43.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally some orderly comes in and stuffs my Albert
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.82,1:35:46.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,in an oversized Glad garbage bag
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.29,1:35:49.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and puts him in the alley with the rest of the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.89,1:35:54.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I did you a favor, man. I got him out.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.03,1:35:56.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want 50 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.39,1:36:22.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Is that all of him? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.66,1:36:25.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You want him? $3,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.37,1:36:37.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,He's gone. He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.17,1:36:40.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.78,1:36:44.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.95,1:36:49.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am telling you they are murdering us
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.12,1:36:50.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and we are letting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.55,1:36:52.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.25,1:36:53.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We're gonna die very soon
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.99,1:36:56.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,unless you get off your fucking asses and fight back."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.54,1:37:15.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Emma's in there waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.32,1:37:31.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, two bites. Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.29,1:37:35.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- No. - Don't make me break out the yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.17,1:37:42.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- One more. - Have you talked to your brother yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.14,1:37:53.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I remember that about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.85,1:37:57.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't talk to the people you love most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.89,1:38:06.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You want me to get better and I'm not getting better
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.46,1:38:09.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and I feel so fucking guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.44,1:38:24.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a lunch meeting with Bill Blass on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.61,1:38:27.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- Fancy. - Mm...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.95,1:38:30.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll call with my regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.78,1:38:34.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.25,1:38:36.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Making a date with you two months from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.85,1:38:39.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been invited to speak at Yale's Gay Week.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.36,1:38:42.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And we're going. Remember how I told you they have those dances there now?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.99,1:38:45.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You're my date.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.79,1:39:17.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I want you to live so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.36,1:39:19.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.47,1:39:28.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, please, God. Give us one more year.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.24,1:39:34.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I promise I'll eat my spinach.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.34,1:40:02.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I am taking care
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.00,1:40:03.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,of more victims of this disease
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.97,1:40:05.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,than anyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.61,1:40:07.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,We have more frozen blood samples
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.78,1:40:09.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,more data of every kind
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.91,1:40:12.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,and much more experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.12,1:40:18.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Brookner, the government's position is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.62,1:40:22.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,There are $5 million in the pipeline for which we have received
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.46,1:40:25.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,over $55 million worth of requests.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.09,1:40:28.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,5 million doesn't seem quite right for some 2,000 cases.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.86,1:40:33.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The government spent 3 million investigating seven deaths from Tylenol
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.80,1:40:36.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,- We're entering the third year. - We voted to reject
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.60,1:40:39.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,your application for funding.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.07,1:40:41.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.54,1:40:43.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.01,1:40:45.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,The direction of the research you're suggesting
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.25,1:40:48.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,is imprecise and unfocused.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.11,1:40:50.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it is, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.68,1:40:52.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't know what's going on any more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.95,1:40:56.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Could you tell me precisely why you're blocking my efforts?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.46,1:40:59.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Brookner. There are now other investigators.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.13,1:41:02.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,This is no longer only your disease, though you seem to think it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.36,1:41:03.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I do, do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.80,1:41:06.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're here to take it away from me, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.60,1:41:09.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you in on a little secret, Doctor.
